e%20Reyes%2C%2027%2C%20who%20moved%20from%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia%2C%20to%20Helsinki%2C%20one%20of%20the%20happiest%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Helsinki%20without%20ever%20visiting%20the%20country%20because%20I%20read%20that%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-finland-happiest-place-never-visited-2023-12%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20happiest%20place%20on%20earth%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Finland%20from%20my%20hometown%20in%20Bogot%C3%A1%2C%20Colombia%2C%20I%20experienced%20a%20completely%20different%20lifestyle%20from%20what%20I%20had%20been%20used%20to.%20I%20knew%20that%20the%20weather%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20change%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20other%20interesting%20surprises%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinnish%20people%20don't%20wear%20shoes%20in%20the%20office%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20not%20unusual%20to%20take%20off%20your%20shoes%20before%20entering%20someone's%20house%2C%20most%20Finnish%20offices%20also%20have%20a%20no-shoe%20policy.%20Some%20offices%20will%20have%20%26quot%3Bindoor%20shoes%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20colleagues%20will%20wear%20socks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20from%20Colombia%2C%20I%20didn't%20bring%20any%20socks%20since%20I%20came%20from%20a%20warmer%20climate.%20I%20had%20to%20go%20out%20and%20buy%20interesting%2C%20fun%20socks%20with%20different%20fabrics%20and%20styles%20for%20the%20workplace.%20I%20bought%20some%20Pikachu%20socks%20and%20socks%20with%20funny%20logos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20around%20the%20world%20style%20their%20wardrobes%20for%20the%20workplace%2C%20but%20in%20Finland%2C%20we%20style%20socks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaked%20saunas%20with%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20are%20normal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20strong%20culture%20of%20saunas%20in%20Finland.%20Everyone%20usually%20has%20a%20sauna%20in%20their%20house%20or%20their%20residential%20building%20and%20many%20offices%20even%20have%20one%20at%20their%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interesting%20thing%2C%20which%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20until%20I%20moved%2C%20is%20that%20it's%20the%20cultural%20norm%20to%20enter%20the%20sauna%20naked.%20People%20will%20chat%20and%20talk%20in%20the%20sauna%2C%20completely%20undressed.%20It's%20normal%20because%20the%20naked%20body%20is%20not%20considered%20taboo%20here.%20People%20have%20a%20high%20level%20of%20respect%20and%20decorum%20for%20each%20other%2C%20so%20there%20are%20no%20awkward%20stares%20or%20gawping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20I%20have%20only%20used%20my%20building's%20sauna.%20It's%20not%20mandatory%20to%20go%20undressed%2C%20so%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20I%20would%20wear%20swimming%20trunks.%20Over%20time%2C%20I've%20become%20more%20comfortable%20going%20naked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInvesting%20in%20good%20blinds%20is%20a%20necessity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20summers%2C%20especially%20in%20July%20and%20August%2C%20there%20is%20barely%20any%20darkness%20and%20the%20sun%20is%20always%20shining.%20It%20can%20be%202%20a.m.%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20glaring%20sun%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20surprising%20how%20much%20time%20and%20effort%20people%20spend%20in%20choosing%20the%20right%20blinds%20and%20curtains.%20But%20I%20soon%20realized%20without%20the%20proper%20materials%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20sleep.%20I%20had%20to%20put%20extra%20curtains%20on%20my%20blinds%20so%20that%20I%20could%20sleep%20well%20and%20not%20have%20a%20detrimental%20impact%20on%20my%20sleep%20hygiene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20is%20also%20when%20people%20are%20always%20out%20because%20the%20sun%20is%20a%20rarity.%20When%20I%20first%20moved%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20manage%20the%20amount%20of%20light%20we%20got%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20sun%20didn't%20set%20for%20a%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBear%20and%20reindeer%20meat%20are%20often%20served%20at%20markets%20and%20restaurants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20of%20the%20world%2C%20especially%20where%20I%20come%20from%2C%20they%20don't%20have%20access%20to%20bear%20or%20reindeer%20meat.%20But%20here%2C%20they%20serve%20it%20in%20the%20markets%20and%20restaurants%20as%20a%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20prepare%20the%20reindeer%20sausage%20as%20kebabs.%20Reindeer%20meat%20tasted%20good%20to%20me%2C%20very%20tender%20and%20rich%20earthy%20flavor.%20I%20haven't%20tried%20bear%20meat%20yet%2C%20but%20I%20heard%20it%20has%20a%20similar%20texture%20to%20pork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20my%20understanding%20that%20it%20is%20a%20popular%20dish%20in%20Finland%20and%20is%20often%20served%20during%20the%20winter%20holidays.%20I%20see%20reindeer%20meat%20mostly%20sold%20in%20local%20markets%20throughout%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20still%20many%20options%20for%20vegetarians%20and%20vegans%2C%20so%20the%20culinary%20scene%20is%20evolving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20public%20transport%20is%20so%20easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20impressed%20by%20the%20wealth%20of%20options%20for%20public%20transport%20and%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20get%20everywhere.%20In%20Helsinki%2C%20you%20can%20choose%20between%20the%20tram%2C%20metro%2C%20trains%2C%20and%20renting%20bikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Colombia%2C%20we%20only%20had%20the%20metro%20and%20the%20bus%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20didn't%20go%20everywhere.%20Here%2C%20the%20transport%20goes%20directly%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20central%20station%20where%20all%20the%20modes%20of%20transportation%20converge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20I%20bike%20everywhere%2C%20but%20since%20it's%20so%20cold%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20I%20opt%20for%20these%20other%20modes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinnish%20people%20are%20happy%20to%20shop%20secondhand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20people%20are%20fashionable%20and%20dress%20well%20here%2C%20they%20don't%20mind%20wearing%20second-hand%20clothes%20as%20an%20environmentally-friendly%20option.%20People%20don't%20seem%20to%20care%20as%20much%20about%20wearing%20expensive%20clothes%20and%20prioritize%20comfort%20and%20their%20personal%20preferences%20over%20name%20brands%20or%20the%20price%20tag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Colombia%2C%20it%20would%20be%20unusual%20to%20wear%20secondhand%20or%20thrift%20clothing.%20I%20don't%20even%20think%20we%20have%20that%20many%20stores%20to%20go%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESave%20dinner%20for%20the%20second%20date%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Finns%20use%20similar%20dating%20apps%20like%20Hinge%20or%20Bumble%20the%20way%20others%20do%20around%20the%20world%2C%20one%20key%20difference%20is%20how%20they%20treat%20first%20dates.%20I%20was%20warned%20early%20on%20that%20going%20to%20a%20nice%20restaurant%20on%20a%20first%20date%20may%20be%20considered%20%26quot%3Btoo%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Colombia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20first%20dates%20tend%20to%20be%20a%20nice%20dinner%20at%20a%20restaurant.%20Here%2C%20it's%20recommended%20to%20go%20to%20bars%20and%20caf%C3%A9s%20on%20the%20first%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-finland-happiest-place-on-earth-what-its-like-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706264837000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b23c68f4b446f3be9cf8e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-finland-happiest-place-on-earth-what-its-like-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jorge%20Reyes%20moved%20to%20Finland%20because%20it%20was%20the%20happiest%20place%20on%20earth.%20He%20loves%20Helsinki