zation%20to%20advance%20and%20not%20regress%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98people%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20might%20argue%20that%20it%20is%20pointless%20to%20discuss%20what%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kritischestudenten.nl%2Fblog%2Fpolitiek%2Fthe-function-of-the-university-in-a-time-of-crisis-noam-chomsky-1969%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efunction%20a%20university%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20may%20serve%20in%20a%20constitutional%20learning%20crisis%20at%20a%20time%20when%20education%20is%20directly%20and%20only%20linked%20to%20requirements%20of%20%E2%80%98certification%E2%80%99.%20Teaching%20and%20research%20are%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20constrained%20to%20serve%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20need%20and%20for%20an%20intellectual%20elite%20to%20remain%20safe%20in%20ivory%20castles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scope%20for%20first-time%20learners%20to%20access%20quality%20higher%20education%20is%20narrowing%20and%20growing%20more%20restricted%20by%20the%20day.%C2%A0%20This%20is%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kritischestudenten.nl%2Fblog%2Fpolitiek%2Fthe-function-of-the-university-in-a-time-of-crisis-noam-chomsky-1969%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENoam%20Chomsky%20argued%20back%20in%201969%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eone%20element%20in%20the%20unending%20struggle%20to%20achieve%20a%20more%20just%20and%20humane%20social%20order%20will%20be%20the%20effort%20to%20remove%20the%20barriers%20%2C%20whether%20they%20be%20economic%2C%20ideological%2C%20or%20political%20%2C%20that%20stand%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20particular%20forms%20of%20individual%20self%20fulfillment%20and%20collective%20action%20that%20the%20university%20should%20make%20possible%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20deeply%20unequal%20education%20landscape%20faces%20a%20growing%20problem%20of%20elitism%20in%20academia%20(concentrated%20in%20some%20private%20institutions)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20an%20acute%20deficiency%20of%20intellectual%20talent%20that%20also%20plagues%20other%20public%20institutions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20encouragement%20to%20%E2%80%98mediocrity%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20university%2C%20college%2C%20or%20even%20a%20school%2C%20personifies%20the%20state%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20education%20system%20today.%20Students%2C%20scholars%2C%20and%20even%20young%20research%20enthusiasts%20are%20perfectly%20okay%20in%20devoting%20their%20entire%20learning%20cycle%20or%20career%20to%20trivial%20modifications%20of%20what%20has%20already%20been%20known%2C%20produced%2C%20and%20validated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20what%20classical%20Marxists%20would%20call%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-all-universities-should-be-teaching-the-constitution-111611581579397.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98social%20reproduction%20thesis%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20they%20are%20doing%20the%20same%20thing%20repeatedly%20with%20minor%20tweaks%20and%20changes.%20The%20publication%20industry%20encourages%20it%20in%20a%20deeply%20entrenched%2C%20neo-liberal%20model%20of%20%E2%80%98educative%E2%80%99%20commodification.%20Any%20hope%20for%20a%20widespread%20reform%20seems%20delusionary%20in%20the%20current%20political%20climate.%20This%20makes%20the%20constitutional%20learning%20crisis%20even%20worse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20one%20is%20being%20trained%20as%20a%20corporate%20executive%2C%20a%20shoemaker%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20an%20economist%2C%20or%20an%20architect%2C%20knowledge%20in%20constitutionalism%20must%20be%20part%20of%20one%E2%80%99s%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20might%20not%20just%20help%20in%20one%20understanding%20elements%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20founding%20constitutional%20charter%2C%20for%20the%20legal%20(and%20moral)%20value%20it%20may%20provide%2C%20but%20its%20knowledge%20may%20also%20enable%20an%20awareness%20of%20our%20own%20social%2C%20cultural%2C%20political%2C%20and%20economic%20state%20of%20being.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20misplaced%20reading%20of%20fundamental%20rights%20and%20duties%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20last%20independence%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fnews_updates%2Fpms-address-at-azadi-ke-amrit-mahotsav-se-swarnim-bharat-ke-ore-pogramme%2F%3Fcomment%3Ddisable%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Espeech%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20remarked%3A%20%E2%80%9CFriends%2C%20%E2%80%A6.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20(also)%20have%20to%20admit%20that%20in%20the%2075%20years%20after%20Independence%2C%20a%20malaise%20has%20afflicted%20our%20society%2C%20our%20nation%20and%20all%20of%20us.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20that%20we%20turned%20away%20from%20our%20duties%20and%20did%20not%20give%20them%20primacy.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%2075%20years%2C%20we%20only%20kept%20talking%20about%20rights%2C%20fighting%20for%20rights%20and%20wasting%20our%20time.%20The%20issue%20of%20rights%20may%20be%20right%20to%20some%20extent%20in%20certain%20circumstances%2C%20but%20neglecting%20one%E2%80%99s%20duties%20completely%20has%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20keeping%20India%20vulnerable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Frights-duties-and-the-constitution%2Farticle30915951.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20conflation%20of%20rights%20and%20duties%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20subject%20much%20debated%20and%20critiqued%20in%20moral%20philosophy%20too%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20make%20note%20of%20acclaimed%20philosopher%20and%20jurist%2C%20Thomas%20Scanlon%E2%80%99s%20advice%20i.e.%20centred%20on%20a%20better%20need%20to%20understand%20and%20study%20the%20role%20of%20interests%2C%20safeguarding%20both%20%E2%80%98rights%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98duties%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20ascertain%20the%20interests%20of%20those%20who%20critique%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frights-duties-and-why-pm-modis-assessment-of-their-connection-is-wrong%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20normative%20significance%20of%20right%20or%20duties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20context%20with%20the%20founding%20principles%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%2C%20as%20Gautam%20Bhatia%20has%20illustrated%20in%20his%20book%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Transformative%20Constitution%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20there%20were%20two%20important%20concerns%20for%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20when%20it%20came%20to%20writing%20the%20two%20chapters%20in%20defining%20our%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20was%20that%20under%20the%20colonial%20regime%2C%20Indians%20were%20treated%20as%20subjects.%20Their%20interests%20did%20not%20count%2C%20their%20voices%20were%20unheard%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20they%20were%20treated%20as%20less%20than%20human.%20The%20key%20role%20of%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20charter%C2%A0%20was%2C%20in%20Bhatia%E2%80%99s%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20stand%20as%20a%20bulwark%20against%20dehumanisation%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvery%20human%20being%2C%20no%20matter%20who%20they%20were%20or%20what%20they%20did%2C%20had%20a%20claim%20to%20%E2%80%98basic%20dignity%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98equality%E2%80%99%20that%20no%20state%20could%20take%20away%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20provocation%E2%80%9D.%20One%20needn%E2%80%99t%20perform%20any%20%E2%80%98duty%E2%80%99%20to%20become%20eligible%20or%20qualify%20for%20having%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Erole%20of%20rights%2C%20as%20Bhatia%20argues%2C%20was%20to%20stand%20against%20hierarchy.%20Through%20guarantees%20against%20forced%20labour%2C%20untouchability%20and%20discriminatory%20access%20to%20public%20spaces%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20fundamental%20rights%20were%20meant%20to%20%E2%80%9Cplay%20an%20equalising%20and%20democratising%20role%20throughout%20society%2C%20and%20to%20protect%20individuals%20against%20the%20depredations%20visited%20on%20them%20by%20their%20fellow%20human-beings%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frights-duties-and-why-pm-modis-assessment-of-their-connection-is-wrong%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20moral%20compass%20of%20rights%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20enshrined%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20charter%2C%20any%20language%20emphasising%20the%20role%20of%C2%A0%20just%20%E2%80%98duties%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20own%20speech%20and%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20reflects%2C%20will%20damage%20the%20rights%20based%20discourse%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERights%20and%20corresponding%20duties%20remain%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%20Prioritising%20just%20one%2C%20or%20pitting%20one%20side%20against%20the%20other%2C%20will%20not%20do.%20Unfortunately%2C%20what%20we%20see%20now%20is%20a%20kinship%20projection%20of%20%E2%80%98citizen%20duties%E2%80%99%20being%20pegged%20higher%20than%20constitutionally%20safeguarded%20fundamental%20rights%20that%20have%20been%20systematically%20bulldozed%20by%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20understand%20the%20constitution%20and%20preserve%20it%2C%20in%20its%20living%20essence%2C%20universalising%20its%20teachings%2C%20and%20principles%20remains%20key.%20This%20will%20help%20in%20making%20the%20constitution%20more%20accessible%20to%20all%20of%20those%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20republic%20(especially%20the%20young).%20It%20is%20important%20that%20while%20celebrating%20its%20innate%20living%20essence%20every%20January%2026%2C%20we%20refrain%20from%20turning%20it%20into%20a%20symbolic%20political%20event%20being%20utilised%20narrowly%20for%20inviting%20foreign%20dignitaries%20to%20serve%20foreign%20policy%20means%20and%20ends%2C%20while%20making%20the%20founding%20charter%20and%20its%20constitutional%20memory%20redundant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20what%20we%20see%20happening%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20economics%20and%20director%2C%20the%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%2C%20Jindal%20School%20of%20Liberal%20Arts%20and%20Humanities%2C%20OP%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706264709000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funiversalising-our-constitutional-values-is-the-key-to-preserving-its-essence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20India%20celebrates%20its%2075th%20Republic%20Day%2C%20we%20must%20refresh%20the%20essence%20of%20our%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20basic%20structure%20and%20moral%20values%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Funiversalising-our-constitutional-values-is-the-key-to-preserving-its-essence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenya%20court%20blocks%20police%20deployment%20to%20Haiti%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706264531000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3A05%2Fproduction%2F_132435841_gettyimages-1236226686.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68090488%22%2C%22