hether%20he%20would%20now%20be%20comfortable%20with%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20as%20an%20alliance%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20hypothetical%20questions%20which%20I%20would%20not%20like%20to%20answer.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20end%20to%20such%20speculations%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Mr%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20scoffed%20at%20reports%20in%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%20speculating%20that%20if%20Nitish%20Kumar%20made%20a%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20could%20switch%20sides%20and%20seek%20an%20alliance%20with%20RJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20the%20current%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20baseless%20reports%20which%20erode%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20fourth%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20fumed%20Mr%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan's%20comments%20came%20amidst%20a%20strong%20buzz%20that%20Kumar%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20was%20now%20done%20with%20the%20anti-BJP%20coalition%20and%20exploring%20possibilities%20with%20his%20old%20ally%20which%20he%20had%20dumped%20less%20than%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20neither%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JD(U)%20nor%20the%20BJP%20has%20dropped%20a%20clear%20hint%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJD(U)'s%20political%20advisor%20and%20spokesperson%20KC%20Tyagi%20has%20been%20asserting%20that%20his%20party%20saw%20itself%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20architect%20of%20INDIA%26quot%3B%20and%20wanted%20to%20remain%20a%20part%20of%20the%20coalition%20though%20developments%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab%20were%20a%20cause%20for%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20president%20Samrat%20Choudhary%2C%20who%20met%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20party's%20principal%20strategist%2C%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20asserted%20that%20the%20talks%20centred%20around%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20top%20leaders%20