ints%20in%20nearly%202%2C000%20traffic%20tickets%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProvincial%20authorities%20launched%20a%20probe%20following%20a%20complaint%20from%20a%20truck%20driver%20who%20was%20fined%20%2470.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECash-strapped%20local%20governments%20in%20China%20have%20been%20handing%20out%20random%20fines%20to%20boost%20their%20finances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20local%20government%20in%20northern%20China%20was%20busted%20for%20faking%20signatures%20on%20nearly%202%2C000%20traffic%20tickets%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fhudong%2Fducha%2F202401%2Fcontent_6926978.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20State%20Council%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20country's%20cabinet%2C%20announced%20on%20January%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHebei%20provincial%20authorities%20launched%20a%20probe%20into%20She%20County%20after%20a%20truck%20driver%2C%20identified%20by%20his%20last%20name%20Xu%2C%20filed%20a%20complaint.%20She%20County%20is%20in%20Hebei%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXu%20said%20he%20was%20fined%20500%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20%2470.40%2C%20on%20the%20spot%20after%20a%20cargo%20of%20coal%20he%20was%20carrying%20spilled%20over%2C%20per%20the%20Council's%20announcement.%20However%2C%20he%20said%20he%20didn't%20receive%20official%20notice%20of%20his%20offense%2C%20and%20he%20said%20he%20didn't%20sign%20or%20provide%20his%20fingerprints%20for%20any%20documentation.%20It's%20unclear%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20found%20that%20She%20County's%20transport%20bureau%20forged%20Xu's%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20not%20all.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20bureau%20faked%20signatures%20and%20fingerprints%20on%201%2C964%20of%20the%202%2C099%20traffic%20tickets%20it%20issued%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20State%20Council%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20have%20suspended%20four%20law%20enforcement%20officers%20and%20punished%20five%20senior%20bureau%20officials%20for%20the%20forgeries%2C%20the%20State%20Council%20said%20in%20its%20statement.%20It%20didn't%20state%20what%20the%20punishment%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20State%20Council%20did%20not%20state%20the%20motivations%20behind%20She%20County's%20forgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fttarticle%2Fp%2Fshow%3Fid%3D2309404991981154861954%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECCTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20linked%20the%20case%20to%20the%20use%20of%20excessive%20and%20arbitrary%20fines%20to%20generate%20revenue%20in%20some%20regions%20%E2%80%94%20a%20practice%20that%20is%20almost%20an%20%26quot%3Bopen%20secret%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Shanghai%20was%20fined%205%2C000%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%20or%20%24704%2C%20for%20serving%20shredded%20cucumber%20without%20a%20license%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-06-11%2Fesoteric-fines-pile-up-as-china-s-provinces-hunt-for-revenue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20warned%20that%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fzhengce%2Fcontent%2F2022-08%2F17%2Fcontent_5705729.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecracking%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20such%20practices%20to%20generate%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20come%20as%20China's%20cash-strapped%20local%20governments%20have%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fchina-10t-hidden-debt-crisis-time-bomb-biden-warned-of-2023-8.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20%2410%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20so-called%20local%20government%20financing%20vehicle%2C%20or%20LGFV%2C%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20local%20governments%20have%20been%20struggling%20to%20repay%20their%20LGFV%20debt.%20It's%20another%20risk%20to%20China's%20economy%2C%20which%20has%20been%20struggling%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noo