%20Republic%20Day%20parade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706259905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F2BF5%2Fproduction%2F_132435211_gettyimages-1953607518-594x594.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68091821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20year%2C%20the%20country%20celebrates%20the%20day%20its%20constitution%20came%20into%20effect%20with%20a%20grand%20spectacle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68091821%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68091821.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-68091821.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Quota%20Stir%3A%20Jarange%20Patil%20Leads%20Massive%20March%20to%20Mumbai%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26123204%2FScreenshot-2024-01-25-at-9.52.55%25E2%2580%25AFPM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20nation%20witnessed%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%2C%20another%20significant%20event%20unfolded%20in%20Maharashtra%20%E2%80%93%20a%20massive%20Maratha%20%3Cem%3Emorcha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(protest)%20led%20by%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil.%20Starting%20from%20Jalna%20on%20January%2020%2C%20this%20protest%20traversed%20through%20Ahmednagar%20and%20is%20set%20to%20reach%20Mumbai%20on%20January%2026.%20Massive%20crowds%20were%20seen%20taking%20part%20in%20this%20protest%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Maratha%20reservation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatil%20also%20issued%20an%20ultimatum%20saying%20that%20he%20will%20go%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20starting%20January%2026%20in%20Mumbai%20if%20their%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20met.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Marathas%20have%20carried%20out%20more%20than%2050%20protests%20between%202016%20and%202018.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20M.G.%20Gaikwad%20Commission%20recommended%20including%20the%20community%20in%20the%20Socially%20and%20Economically%20Backward%20Classes%20category.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20unanimously%20passed%20a%20bill%20granting%20the%20Maratha%20community%2016%25%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%20in%20November%20that%20year.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20citing%20the%20Indra%20Sawhney%20judgment%2C%20ruled%20that%20reservations%20should%20not%20surpass%2050%25%20and%20thus%20struck%20down%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20in%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20agitation%20for%20Maratha%20reservations%20was%20then%20revived%20in%20September%202023.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatil%20gained%20prominence%20in%20September%20last%20year%20after%20the%20Maharashtra%20police%20lathi-charged%20on%20a%20Maratha%20protest%20in%20Jalna.%20Despite%20breaking%20a%2017-day%20hunger%20strike%20after%20a%20meeting%20with%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20unanswered%20ultimatums%20led%20him%20to%20declare%20this%20morcha%20from%20Jalna%20to%20Mumbai%20via%20Ahmednagar%20and%20Pune.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20Marathas%20demanded%20that%20they%20be%20included%20in%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20category%20by%20granting%20all%20Marathas%20a%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificate.%20The%20OBCs%20are%20opposed%20to%20giving%20Marathas%20any%20space%20within%20the%20reservation%20system%20and%20the%20conflicting%20demands%20have%20sparked%20protests%20across%20various%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra.%20These%20were%20led%20by%20Chagan%20Bhujbal%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(NCP%E2%80%99s)%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction.%20Some%20say%20Bhujbal%20is%20trying%20to%20project%20himself%20as%20a%20future%20leader%20of%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20the%20demographics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Human%20Development%20Survey%20(IHDS)%20data%20shows%20that%2C%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%2032.8%25%20of%20the%20populations%20belongs%20to%20the%20OBC%20category%2C%2026.6%25%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%209.7%25%20are%20from%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%2C%209.3%25%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(ST)%2C%206.6%25%20constitute%20Other%20Upper%20Castes%20(OUC)%2C%205.8%25%20are%20Muslims%2C%20and%201.8%25%20are%20Brahmins.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20Marathas%20constituting%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20population%2C%20especially%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20disparities%20exist.%20Urban%20statistics%20show%20only%2012%25%20of%20Marathas%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20and%20poorest%E2%80%9D%20categories%2C%20with%2070%25%20belonging%20to%20the%20affluent%20class.%20Educational%20performance%20and%20economic%20strata%20indicate%20a%20robust%20presence%20putting%20them%20second%20only%20to%20the%20Brahmin%20community.%20However%2C%20as%20per%20a%20research%20paper%20by%20Sumeet%20Mhaskar%2C%20IHDS%20data%20indicates%20that%2038%25%20of%20Marathas%20in%20rural%20areas%20fall%20into%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%20and%20poorest%E2%80%9D%20category%2C%20revealing%20that%20the%20community%20faces%20challenges%20primarily%20in%20villages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%20a%20dominant%20community%2C%20Marathas%20faced%20economic%20setbacks%20post-1990%2C%20with%20the%20closure%20of%20mills%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20economic%20shift%20forced%20many%20into%20poverty%2C%20prompting%20a%20return%20to%20villages%20where%20agriculture%20was%20no%20longer%20profitable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEconomic%20vulnerabilities%20led%20Marathas%20to%20rely%20on%20public%20institutions%2C%20facing%20tough%20competition%20for%20open%20category%20seats%20due%20to%20financial%20constraints.%20Exorbitant%20fees%20in%20private%20institutions%20and%20unauthorised%20commissions%20added%20to%20their%20challenges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Counter-protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20OBC%20community%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Bhujbal%2C%20has%20vehemently%20opposed%20the%20proposition%20to%20grant%20Marathas%20OBC%20reservation.%20Bhujbal%2C%20a%20key%20political%20figure%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20the%20potential%20adverse%20impact%20on%20the%20existing%20300%2B%20OBC%20communities%20if%20Marathas%20are%20included%20in%20this%20category.%20He%20argues%20that%20such%20inclusion%20would%20disproportionately%20affect%20other%20OBC%20groups%20and%20stands%20firm%20against%20endorsing%20the%20proposal.%20This%20opposition%20from%20the%20OBCs%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20significant%20hurdle%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20Maratha%20reservation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShinde%20has%20attempted%20to%20placate%20Patil%2C%20but%20his%20alliance%20with%20OBC%20leaders%20like%20Bhujbal%20has%20lead%20to%20a%20deadlock.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20the%20question%20remains%3A%20Will%20Maratha%20reservation%20be%20granted%2C%20or%20will%20Patil%E2%80%99s%20agitation%20challenge%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%3F%20Watch%20the%20video%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAOqRYdaMNuM%3Fsi%3DdjPS2LpSj6sNOzpK%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706259644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26123204%2FScreenshot-2024-01-25-at-9.52.55%25E2%2580%25AFPM.jpg%2