%20smile%20flickered%20across%20her%20face%3A%20%E2%80%9CShall%20I%20just%20ask%20for%20coffee%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHabib%20had%20hesitatingly%20called%20that%20morning%20to%20ask%20if%20they%20could%20come%20and%20see%20her%20to%20discuss%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CHave%20there%20been%20more%20arrests%3F%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20had%20asked%2C%20and%20had%20been%20assured%20that%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20case.%20She%20had%20agreed%20to%20see%20them%20in%20her%20home%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20rose%20now%20to%20ask%20someone%20in%20the%20kitchen%20for%20coffee.%20Habib%20regarded%20the%20titles%20on%20the%20bookshelves.%20Jamal%20gazed%20at%20the%20strange%20painting%20behind%20her%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coffee%20tray%20arrived%20soon%20with%20coffee%20in%20a%20French%20press%2C%20four%20ceramic%20mugs%2C%20a%20milk%20pot%20and%20a%20sugar%20bowl%20on%20the%20side.%20The%20men%20watched%20patiently%20as%20Tara%20poured%20coffee%2C%20and%20then%20asked%20each%20one%20of%20them%20if%20they%20wanted%20milk%20and%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20what%20is%20your%20full%20name%3F%E2%80%9D%20ASI%20Achche%20Lal%20asked%20as%20he%20reached%20for%20his%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTara%20Azad%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CStir%20it%20%E2%80%93%20so%20what%20did%20the%20two%20reports%20say%2C%20exactly%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EASI%20Achche%20Lal%20put%20his%20coffee%20down%20and%20took%20his%20notebook%20out.%20%E2%80%9CI%20spoke%20to%20the%20doctor%20also%20when%20I%20went%20to%20get%20the%20reports.%20She%20said%20that%20he%20had%20collapsed%20and%20fallen%20on%20the%20counter%2C%20and%20hit%20his%20head%20on%20the%20heavy%20steam%20iron.%20Then%2C%20because%20of%20his%20fall%2C%20the%20whole%20counter%20crashed%20to%20the%20floor%2C%20together%20with%20the%20steam%20iron%2C%20and%20Rahman%20miyan%20himself%2C%20and%20he%20probably%20hit%20his%20head%20a%20second%20time%20on%20the%20iron.%20There%20were%20several%20deep%20cuts%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20bleeding%20also%2C%20but%20that%20was%20not%20the%20cause%20of%20death.%20In%20fact%2C%20she%20said%20that%20there%20was%20some%20internal%20bleeding%20also%2C%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20that%20serious%20and%20again%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20cause%20of%20death.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20so%20much%20blood%20probably%20because%20he%20took%20Ecosprin%2C%20blood%20thinning%20medicine%20for%20his%20heart.%20I%20checked%20at%20his%20home%2C%20when%20I%20heard%20about%20the%20excessive%20bleeding%20in%20the%20post%20mortem%20report%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib%20proudly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWaah%2C%20Habib.%20You%20think%20of%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tara%20said.%20Habib%20smiled%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDetective%20Habibi%20is%20the%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jamal%20patted%20him%20affectionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20how%20did%20Rahman%20miyan%20die%20then%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20the%20doctor%20said%20that%20reports%20shows%20that%20he%20had%20some%20lung%20infection.%20There%20was%20a%20patch%20on%20the%20lungs.%20He%20also%20had%20a%20problem%20of%20shortness%20of%20breath.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20called%20Dyspnea%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20added%20Habib%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20he%20was%20diabetic%20also%2C%20madam.%20Normally%20he%20was%20very%20careful.%20But%20the%20last%20few%20days%20his%20Mrs%20was%20not%20at%20home%2C%20so%20he%20had%20been%20eating%20a%20little%20greasy%20food.%20Viscera%20report%20shows%20very%20high%20blood%20acid%20levels%2C%20sugar%20levels%20and%20key%E2%80%A6ketones%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20checked%20his%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20lung%20infection%20and%20all%20this%20bad%20food%20caused%20diabetic%20keto-acid-osis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamal%2C%20Habib%20and%20Tara%20simultaneously%20Googled%20diabetic%20ketoacidosis.%20%E2%80%9CSerious%20diabetic%20complication%2C%20where%20there%20is%20excess%20blood%20acid%2C%20triggered%20by%20infection%20in%20the%20body.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20this%20is%20why%20we%20tell%20you%20to%20be%20careful%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20doctor%20told%20me%20that%20he%20had%20an%20infection%2C%20then%20he%20had%20sugar%20and%20that%20led%20to%20this%20condition.%20He%20went%20into%20a%20coma%20and%20passed%20away%20after%20a%20few%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20had%20been%20thorough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20he%20fell%20unconscious%2C%20and%20then%20lay%20in%20a%20coma%20all%20night%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Jamal%20%E2%80%9CProbably%20when%20Salman%20went%20in%20he%20was%20actually%20still%20alive.%20If%20Salman%20had%20attended%20to%20him%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20post%20mortem%20report%2C%20death%20occurred%20early%20in%20the%20morning.%20Whereas%20he%20must%20have%20slipped%20into%20a%20coma%20around%20midnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20sipped%20coffee%20in%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20why%20did%20he%20have%20sugar%3F%20He%20was%20always%20so%20careful%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Tara%20suddenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20he%20had%20actual%20sugar.%20It%20could%20have%20been%20his%20infection%2C%20injury%20or%20stress%20even%2C%20caused%20by%20Rana%20and%20Kanwal%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJamal%20bhai%2C%20the%20report%20mentions%20high%20sugar%20levels.%20I%20think%20he%20was%20actually%20fed%20%3Cem%3Emeetha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20I%20also%20think%20we%20know%20what%20happened%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%3F%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20looked%20earnestly%20at%20everyone%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETara%20nodded.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20we%20do%20know%20what%20happened.%20Achche%20Lal%20ji%2C%20can%20we%20not%20have%20a%20meeting%20with%20all%20the%20suspects%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20case%20is%20closed%2C%20madam.%20How%20can%20we%20direct%20everyone%20to%20assemble%3F%20Bulbhaddar%20babu%20will%20not%20come%3B%20anyway%20he%20is%20too%20busy.%20If%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%2C%20Kanwal%20and%20Nirmal%20will%20also%20not%20come%2C%20and%20nor%20will%20Shambhu%2C%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20least%20we%20can%20have%20the%20others%3F%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20pleaded%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%20Lal%20ji%2C%20were%20you%20able%20to%20test%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Epateela%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20you%20seized%20from%20the%20madarsa%3F%20asked%20Tara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMadam%2C%20they%20finished%20the%20whole%20pateela%20of%20mutton.%20Then%20washed%20it%20clean.%20What%20was%20there%20to%20test%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20test%20the%20bowl%20Rahman%20miyan%20had%20eaten%20in%3F%20I%20think%20you%E2%80%99d%20have%20found%20remnants%20of%20%3Cem%3Echashni%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20they%20stepped%20out%2C%20Jamal%20and%20Habib%20teased%20Achche%20Lal%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20wanted%20to%20know%20her%20religion%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%3F%20That%20is%20why%20you%20wanted%20to%20know%20her%20surname.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CArre%2C%20no!%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20know%20her%20full%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20is%20true.%20There%20was%20nothing%20in%20the%20house%20to%20indicate%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20Tibetan%20prayer%20flags%20draped%20around%20the%20staircase%20and%20there%20was%20Rumi%20in%20the%20bookcase%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughed%20Jamal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20lots%20of%20detective%20fiction%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Habib.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20asking%20about%20Rahman%20miyan%E2%80%99s%20bowl.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20cut%20her%20off%20when%20she%20was%20talking%20but%20the%20bowl%20had%20also%20crashed%20to%20the%20floor.%20We%20found%20some%20broken%20china%20and%20some%20thick%20%3Cem%3Eshorba%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20floor.%20Who%20was%20going%20to%20scrape%20that%20for%20testing%3F%E2%80%9D%20Achche%20Lal%20sounded%20a%20little%20aggrieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAchche%20uncle%2C%20even%20without%20the%20tests%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20clear%20that%20Rahman%20miyan%20was%20given%20sugar.%20Tara%20ma%E2%80%99am%20and%20I%20both%20know%20what%20has%20happened.%20Please%20get%20everyone%20to%20assemble%20at%20Laadley%E2%80%99s%20shop%3F%E2%80%9D%20Habib%20pressed%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20saheb%20had%20clasped%20his%20hands%20together%20and%20was%20pressing%20the%20back%20of%20his%20left%20palm%20against%20his%20right%20cheek%20in%20a%20new%20stretching%20pose.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20it%20was%20natural%20death%20only.%20Bechaare%20Balabhadra%20babu%20was%20right.%20He%20was%20saying%20it%20must%20be%20some%20illness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20repeatedly%20asking%20us%20to%20close%20the%20investigations%20before%20the%20big%20day%2C%20sir.%20With%20God%E2%80%99s%20blessings%2C%20at%20least%20the%20enquiry%20is%20over%20in%20time.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20fulfil%20our%20duty%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Constable%20Awdhesh%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20one%20small%20thing%20though.%20Rahman%20died%20of%20some%20diabetic%20complication.%20Jamal%20ordered%20a%20pateela%20full%20of%20chashni%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20We%20have%20closed%20this%20enquiry%20because%20post%20mortem%20is%20showing%20natural%20death%2C%20but%20in%20future%20you%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20those%20two.%20We%20cannot%20rule%20out%20broader%20conspiracy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20be%20continued%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahrukh%20Alam%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20write%20a%20murder%20mystery%20for%20a%20very%20lo