21094%5C%22%3Esurge%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Ffar-right-poised-to-score-big-at-next-european-elections-214702%5C%22%3Ewestern%20world%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20support%20these%20parties%2C%20their%20appeal%20can%20be%20baffling%20and%20unsettling.%20They%20appear%20to%20play%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20fears%20and%20offer%20somewhat%20trivial%20answers%20to%20difficult%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20mathematics%20of%20human%20inference%20and%20cognition%20can%20help%20us%20understand%20what%20makes%20this%20a%20winning%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20politics%20largely%20boils%20down%20to%20communication%2C%20the%20mathematics%20of%20communication%20theory%20can%20help%20us%20understand%20why%20voters%20are%20drawn%20to%20parties%20that%20use%20simple%2C%20loud%20messaging%20in%20their%20campaigning%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20how%20they%20get%20away%20with%20using%20highly%20questionable%20messaging.%20Traditionally%2C%20this%20is%20the%20theory%20that%20enables%20us%20to%20listen%20to%20radio%20broadcasts%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fbiography%2FClaude-Shannon%23ref666143%5C%22%3Emake%20telephone%20calls%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20American%20mathematician%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNorbert_Wiener%5C%22%3ENorbert%20Wiener%3C%2Fa%3E%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodreads.com%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F153954.The_Human_Use_of_Human_Beings%5C%22%3Eargue%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20social%20phenomena%20can%20only%20be%20understood%20via%20the%20theory%20of%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWiener%20tried%20to%20explain%20different%20aspects%20of%20society%20by%20evoking%20a%20concept%20in%20science%20known%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fscience%2Fsecond-law-of-thermodynamics%5C%22%3Esecond%20law%20of%20thermodynamics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20essence%2C%20this%20law%20says%20that%20over%20time%2C%20order%20will%20turn%20into%20disorder%2C%20or%2C%20in%20the%20present%20context%2C%20reliable%20information%20will%20be%20overwhelmed%20by%20confusion%2C%20uncertainties%20and%20noise.%20In%20mathematics%2C%20the%20degree%20of%20disorder%20is%20often%20measured%20by%20a%20quantity%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.britannica.com%2Fscience%2Fentropy-physics%5C%22%3Eentropy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20the%20second%20law%20can%20be%20rephrased%20by%20saying%20that%20over%20time%2C%20and%20on%20average%2C%20entropy%20will%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Wiener%E2%80%99s%20arguments%20is%20that%20as%20technologies%20for%20communication%20advance%2C%20people%20will%20circulate%20more%20and%20more%20inessential%20%E2%80%9Cnoisy%E2%80%9D%20information%20(think%20Twitter%2C%20Instagram%20and%20so%20on)%2C%20which%20will%20overshadow%20facts%20and%20important%20ideas.%20This%20is%20becoming%20more%20pronounced%20with%20AI-generated%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20of%20the%20second%20law%20is%20significant%20in%20predicting%20the%20future%20form%20of%20society%20over%20a%20period%20of%20decades.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41598-023-43403-4%5C%22%3Eanother%20aspect%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20communication%20theory%20also%20comes%20into%20play%20in%20the%20more%20immediate%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20analyse%20information%20about%20a%20topic%20of%20interest%2C%20we%20will%20reach%20a%20conclusion%20that%20leaves%20us%2C%20on%20average%2C%20with%20the%20smallest%20uncertainty%20about%20that%20topic.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20our%20thought%20process%20attempts%20to%20minimise%20entropy.%20This%20means%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20when%20two%20people%20with%20opposing%20views%20on%20a%20topic%20are%20presented%20with%20an%20article%20on%20that%20subject%2C%20they%20will%20often%20take%20away%20different%20interpretations%20of%20the%20same%20article%2C%20with%20each%20confirming%20the%20validity%20of%20their%20own%20initial%20view.%20The%20reason%20is%20simple%3A%20interpreting%20the%20article%20as%20questioning%20one%E2%80%99s%20opinion%20will%20inevitably%20raise%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20psychology%2C%20this%20effect%20is%20known%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthedecisionlab.com%2Fbiases%2Fconfirmation-bias%5C%22%3Econfirmation%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20often%20interpreted%20as%20an%20irrational%20or%20illogical%20trait%20of%20our%20behaviour%2C%20but%20we%20now%20understand%20the%20science%20behind%20it%20by%20borrowing%20concepts%20from%20communication%20theory.%20I%20call%20this%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.frontiersin.org%2Farticles%2F10.3389%2Ffpsyg.2022.797904%2Ffull%5C%22%3Etenacious%20Bayesian%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20behaviour%20because%20it%20follows%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplato.stanford.edu%2Fentries%2Fbayes-theorem%2F%5C%22%3EBayes%20theorem%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20probability%20theory%2C%20which%20tells%20us%20how%20we%20should%20update%20our%20perspectives%20of%20the%20world%20as%20we%20digest%20noisy%20or%20uncertain%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20corollary%20of%20this%20is%20that%20if%20someone%20has%20a%20strong%20belief%20in%20one%20scenario%20which%20happens%20to%20represent%20a%20false%20reality%2C%20then%20even%20if%20factual%20information%20is%20in%20circulation%2C%20it%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20for%20that%20person%20to%20change%20their%20belief.%20This%20is%20because%20a%20conversion%20from%20one%20certainty%20to%20another%20typically%20(but%20not%20always)%20requires%20a%20path%20that%20traverses%20uncertainties%20we%20instinctively%20try%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolarised%20society%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20tenacious%20Bayesian%20effect%20is%20combined%20with%20Wiener%E2%80%99s%20second%20law%2C%20we%20can%20understand%20how%20society%20becomes%20polarised.%20The%20second%20law%20says%20there%20will%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20diverging%20information%20and%20noise%20around%20us%2C%20creating%20confusion%20and%20uncertainty.%20We%20are%20drawn%20to%20information%20that%20offers%20greater%20certainty%2C%20even%20if%20it%20is%20flawed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20binary%20issue%2C%20the%20greatest%20uncertainty%20happens%20when%20the%20two%20alternatives%20seem%20equally%20likely%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%20therefore%20difficult%20to%20choose%20between.%20But%20for%20an%20individual%20person%20who%20believes%20in%20one%20of%20the%20two%20alternatives%2C%20the%20path%20of%20least%20uncertainty%20is%20to%20hold%20steady%20on%20that%20belief.%20So%20in%20a%20world%20in%20which%20any%20information%20can%20easily%20be%20disseminated%20far%20and%20wide%20but%20in%20which%20people%20are%20also%20immovable%2C%20society%20can%20easily%20be%20polarised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20are%20the%20leftwing%20populists%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20society%20is%20maximally%20polarised%2C%20then%20we%20should%20find%20populists%20surging%20on%20both%20the%20left%20and%20right%20of%20the%20political%20spectrum.%20And%20yet%20that%20is%20not%20the%20case%20at%20the%20moment.%20The%20right%20is%20more%20dominant.%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20is%2C%20in%20part%2C%20that%20the%20left%20is%20not%20well-positioned%20to%20offer%20certainty.%20Why%3F%20Historically%2C%20socialism%20has%20rarely%20been%20implemented%20in%20running%20a%20country%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20or%20China%20managed%20to%20implement%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20for%20now%2C%20the%20left%20(or%20centrists%2C%20for%20that%20matter)%20also%20seem%20a%20lot%20more%20cautious%20about%20knowingly%20offering%20unrealistic%20answers%20to%20complex%20problems.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20right%20offers%20(often%20false)%20certainty%20with%20confidence.%20It%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20see%20that%20in%20a%20noisy%20environment%2C%20the%20loudest%20are%20heard%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20politics%20plays%20out%20against%20a%20backdrop%20of%20uncertainties%20that%20include%20wars%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20Gaza%20with%20little%20prospect%20of%20exit%20strategies%20in%20sight%3B%20the%20continued%20cost%20of%20living%20crisis%3B%20energy%2C%20food%20and%20water%20insecurity%3B%20migration%3B%20and%20so%20on.%20Above%20all%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20to%20this%20uncertainty%2C%20according%20to%20rightwing%20populists%2C%20is%20to%20blame%20everything%20on%20outsiders.%20Remove%20migrants%20and%20all%20problems%20will%20be%20solved%20%E2%80%93%20and%20all%20uncertainties%20eradicated.%20True%20or%20false%2C%20the%20message%20is%20simple%20and%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conveying%20this%20message%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20instil%20in%20the%20public%20an%20exaggerated%20fear%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20migration%2C%20so%20their%20message%20will%20give%20people%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20certainty.%20What%20if%20there%20are%20no%20outsiders%3F%20Then%20create%20one.%20Use%20the%20culture%20war%20to%20label%20the%20%E2%80%9Cexperts%E2%80%9D%20(judges%2C%20scholars%2C%20etc.)%20as%20the%20enemy%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20populists%20to%20thrive%2C%20society%20needs%20to%20be%20divided%20so%20that%20people%20can%20feel%20certain%20about%20where%20they%20belong%20%E2%80%93%20and%20so%20that%20those%20on%20the%20opposing%20side%20of%20the%20argument%20can%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20there%20are%20rarely%20simple%20solutions%20to%20complex%20issues.%20Indeed%2C%20a%20political%20party%20campaigning%20for%20a%20tough%20migration%20policy%20but%20weak%20climate%20measures%20is%20arguably%20enabling%20mass%20migration%20on%20a%20scale%20unseen%20in%20modern%20history%2C%20because%20climate%20change%20will%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.ch%2Fsrccl%2F%5C%22%3Emany%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20uninhabitable%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWiener%20was%20already%20arguing%20in%201950%20that%20we%20will%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20our%20actions%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20most%20inconvenient%20to%20do%20so.%20Whatever%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20to%20solve%20complex%20societal%20issues%2C%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20implement%20what%20they%20believe%20are%20the%20right%20measures%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20that%20they%20have%20to%20win%20an%20election%20to%20do%20that%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20voters%20respond%20to%20simple%20and%20positive%20messages%20that%20will%20reduce%20the%20uncertainties%20hanging%20over%20their%20thoughts.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F221355%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDorje%20C.%20Brody%2C%20Professor%20of%20Mathematics%2C%20University%20of%20Surrey.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fthe-maths-of-rightwing-populism-easy-answers-confidence-reassuring-certainty-221355%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706255143000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26115436%2FUntitled-design-3-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Frightwing-populist-maths%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20rightwing%20populists%2C%20is%20to%20blame%20everything%20on%20outsiders.%20Remove%20migrants%20and%20all%20problems%20will%20be%20solved%20%E2%80%93%20and%20all%20uncertainties%20eradicated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Frightwing-populist-maths%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRussia%20Can%20Rely%20On%20India%20Because...%26quot%3B%3A%20Putin's%20Huge%20Praise%20For%20PM%20Modi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20heaped%20praises%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20credited%20India%20for%20pursuing%20an%20'independent'%20foreign%20policy%20which%20is%20not%20easy%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20Russia-based%20media%20network%20Russia%20Today%20(RT)%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20interacting%20with%20university%20students%20in%20Kaliningrad%20Region%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20'Russian%20Student%20Day'%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20rates%20of%20economic%20development%20and%20growth%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20that%20too%20is%20due%20to%20the%20leadership%20qualities%20of%20incumbent%20Prime%20Minister.%20It%20was%20during%20his%20leadership%20that%20India%20reached%20such%20a%20pace%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Putin%20said%20during%20the%20interaction%20as%20per%20the%20translation%20by%20RT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BRussia%20can%20rely%20on%20India%20and%20its%20leadership%20because%20it%20is%20assured%20that%20New%20Delhi%20won't%20play%20'games'%20against%20them%20at%20the%20international%20stage%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20pursuing%20an%20independent%20foreign%20policy%2C%20which%20is%20not%20easy%20in%20today's%20world.%20But%2C%20India%20with%20a%20population%20of%201.5%20billion%20has%20the%20right%20to%20do%20so.%20And%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20that%20right%20is%20being%20realised.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20statement%2C%20it%20is%20important%20from%20the%20point%20of%20organising%20joint%20work%20because%20it%20gives%20us%20the%20opportunity%20to%20forecast%20the%20actions%20of%20our%20partners%20in%20medium%20and%20long%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20important%20in%20practical%20work.%20Can%20we%20rely%20on%20a%20country%20and%20its%20leadership%20to%20cooperate%20or%20will%20it%20take%20decisions%20that%20do%20not%20even%20correspond%20to%20its%20national%20interest.%20With%20India%2C%20such%20games%20don't%20exist%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20President%20also%20lauded%20India's%20'Make%20in%20India'%20initiative%20and%20said%20that%20Russia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20investors%20in%20the%20country%20and%20is%20further%20looking%20forward%20to%20make%20huge%20investments%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20made%20huge%20steps%20in%20development%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20His%20campaign%20'Make%20in%20India'%20has%20been%20heard%20by%20many%20including%20Russia.%20And%20we%20are%20trying%20with%20our%20Indian%20friends%20to%20bring%20to%20life%20all%20these%20plans...the%20largest%20foreign%20investment%20in%20India%20has%20come%20from%20Russia.%20USD%2023%20billion%20was%20invested%20by%20our%20company%20Roseneft%2C%20acquidition%20of%20an%20oil%20refinery%2C%20a%20network%20of%20gas%20stations%2C%20a%20port%20and%20so%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spoke%20about%20India's%20diverse%20culture%20and%20the%20popularity%20of%20Indian%20movies%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20great%20culture.%20It's%20diverse%20and%20colourful.%20Russia%20is%20probably%20the%20few%20places%20around%20the%20world%20where%20Indian%20movies%20are%20broadcast%20on%20national%20television%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Russian%20President%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20was%20on%20a%20visit%20to%20Russia%20from%20December%2025-29%20last%20year%2C%20as%20a%20part%20of%20the%20ongoing%20high-level%20exchanges%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%2C%20the%20EAM%20called%20on%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20Moscow%20and%20held%20discussions%20with%20several%20top%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20visit%2C%20India%20signed%20three%20documents%20relating%20to%20the%20Kudan%20Kulam%20Nuclear%20Power%20Plants%2C%20an%20MoU%20on%20cooperation%20in%20pharmaceuticals%20and%20healthcare%20and%20a%20Protocol%20on%20Foreign%20Office%20Consultation%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706254740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2018-10%2Fbd79osnk_modi-putin-pti_625x300_05_October_18.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-can-rely-on-india-because-vladimir-putins-huge-praise-for-pm-modi-4935190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vladimir%20Putin%20heaped%20praises%20on%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20credited%20India%20for%20pursuing%20an%20'independent'%20foreign%20policy%20which%20is%20not%20easy%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20Russia-based%20media%20network%20Russia%20Today%20(RT)%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-can-rely-on-india-because-vladimir-putins-huge-praise-for-pm-modi-4935190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-can-rely-on-india-because-vladimir-putins-huge-praise-for-pm-modi-4935190%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-can-rely-on-india-because-vladimir-putins-huge-praise-for-pm-modi-4935190%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bollywood%20Movies%20to%20Watch%20on%20Republic%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706254418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107164852%2Cimgsize-55670.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsam-bahadur-to-fighter-movies-to-watch-on-republic-day%2Fphotostory%2F107164852.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107164852.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsam-bahadur-to-fighter-movies-to-watch-on-republic-day%2Fphotostory%2F107164852.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Review%3A%20Karmma%20Calling%20-%20Heavy%20Lifting%20Is%20Left%20To%20Raveena%20Tandon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20murder%20on%20the%20beach%20shakes%20the%20swish%20set%20of%20Alibaug%20out%20of%20its%20self-obsessed%20stupor.%20Posited%20as%20both%20a%20preface%20and%20the%20probable%20final%20act%20of%20%3Cem%3EKarmma%20Calling%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20seven-part%20Hotstar%20Specials%20series%2C%20the%20prelude%20points%20to%20what%20lies%20ahead%20for%20the%20denizens%20of%20the%20seaside%20enclave%20of%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20callously%20amoral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20young%20woman%20with%20vengeance%20on%20her%20mind%20is%20on%20the%20prowl.%20The%20girl's%20prime%20target%20is%20a%201990s%20Bollywood%20diva-turned-socialite%20and%20her%20family.%20Protecting%20her%20turf%20comes%20easy%20to%20the%20obdurate%20matriarch.%20On%20the%20personal%20front%2C%20however%2C%20life%20isn't%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20her.%20Her%20husband%20strays%20and%20gets%20away%20with%20it.%20Her%20children%20do%20not%20see%20eye%20to%20eye%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20life%20goes%20on%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20dark%20secrets%2C%20pent-up%20rage%2C%20extra-marital%20liaisons%2C%20crass%20conspiracies%2C%20fake%20friendships%20and%20brazen%20betrayals%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20and%20upset%20a%20carefully%20constructed%20facade.%20The%20plot%2C%20busy%20and%20overheated%2C%20has%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKarmma%20Calling%3C%2Fem%3E%20moves%20back%20and%20forth%20in%20time%20to%20provide%20the%20context%20for%20the%20tale%20of%20vendetta.%20But%20it%20never%20quite%20shakes%20off%20its%20unremarkable%20by-the-numbers%20approach%20to%20a%20tale%20that%20has%20been%20told%20before.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20episode%2C%20the%20revenge-seeker%20focuses%20her%20attention%20on%20an%20individual%20who%20-%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20them%20-%20wronged%20her%20and%20her%20upright%20dad%20two%20decades%20ago%20and%20went%20unpunished.%20She%20is%20now%20back%20to%20settle%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20toes%20and%20unyielding%2C%20the%20lady%20is%20meticulous%20in%20her%20planning.%20More%20often%20than%20not%2C%20she%20catches%20her%20victims%20unawares%20and%20achieves%20her%20end.%20But%20despite%20the%20plethora%20of%20twists%20and%20turns%20that%20%3Cem%3EKarmma%20Calling%3C%2Fem%3E%20throws%20at%20us%2C%20the%20show%2C%20adapted%20for%20India%20(from%20the%20American%20series%20Revenge)%20and%20directed%20by%20Ruchi%20Narain%2C%20is%20anything%20but%20an%20edge-of-the-seat%20humdinger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fd_UTOLPcRKk%3Fsi%3Du51r3eGjvQ3XsOIT%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revenge%20that%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKarmma%20Calling%3C%2Fem%3E%20served%20is%20cold%20-%20and%20stale.%20The%20picture-perfect%20setting%20and%20the%20glammed-up%20people%20who%20inhabit%20the%20space%20are%20overly%20inert%20when%20they%20aren't%20outright%20stodgy%20and%20dull.%20That%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20show%20is%20wearisome%20all%20the%20way.%20It%20does%20spring%20to%20a%20bit%20of%20life%20now%20and%20then%2C%20but%20the%20truly%20intriguing%2C%20impactful%20moments%20do%20not%20last%20long%20enough%20to%20lend%20heft%20to%20the%20series.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20engagement%20party%20is%20disrupted%20when%20the%20man%20of%20the%20hour%20goes%20missing.%20He%20is%20found%20lifeless%20on%20a%20beach.%20Cut%20to%20six%20months%20earlier.%20The%20comely%20Karma%20Talwar%20(Namrata%20Sheth)%20rents%20and%20then%20buys%20an%20Alibaug%20bungalow%20next%20to%20the%20town's%20most%20famous%20address%2C%20Kothari%20Mansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mansion%20is%20where%20Indrani%20Kothari%20(Raveena%20Tandon)%20lives%20with%20her%20perfidious%20husband%20Kaushal%20(Gaurav%20Sharma)%2C%20Harvard-returned%20son%20Ahaan%20(Varun%20Sood)%20and%20restive%20daughter%20Mira%20(debutante%20Devangshi%20Sen).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kotharis%20are%20ruthless%20power%20players%20hand%20in%20gloves%20with%20other%20moneyed%20manipulators%20of%20their%20ilk.%20But%20all%20isn't%20obviously%20well%20in%20the%20household.%20Karma%20spots%20an%20opportunity%20in%20the%20deepening%20strife%20and%20looks%20for%20a%20vantage%20point%20from%20where%20she%20can%20launch%20her%20mission%20to%20bring%20down%20Indrani%20Kothari's%20family%20and%20business%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20jets%20and%20ostentatious%20houses%2C%20charity%20galas%20and%20polo%20matches%2C%20intimate%20family%20dinners%20and%20flashy%20dandiya%20nights%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20Indrani%20Kothari's%20life.%20The%20sudden%20appearance%20of%20the%20mysterious%20Karma%20Talwar%20puts%20her%20on%20her%20guard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family's%20head%20of%20security%2C%20Sameer%20(Vikramjeet%20Virk)%2C%20and%20Indrani's%20assistant%20Yana%20(Amy%20Aela)%2C%20are%20the%20wary%20lady's%20go-to%20people%20as%20she%20tries%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20has%20brought%20Karma%20Talwar%20to%20Alibaug.%20The%20audience%20obviously%20knows%20what%20she%20is%20up%20to%20so%20we%20are%20always%20a%20step%20ahead%20of%20the%20characters.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarma's%20father%20(Rohit%20Bose%20Roy%20in%20a%20special%20appearance)%20was%20a%20senior%20employee%20of%20the%20company%20owned%20by%20the%20Kotharis.%20Framed%20in%20a%20bank%20loan%20scam%20that%20he%20had%20no%20hand%20in%2C%20his%20life%20and%20career%20were%20ruined.%20Justice%20for%20him%20is%20what%20his%20daughter%20now%20seeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20manner%20of%20people%20-%20a%20top%20lawyer-turned-MP%20(Shataf%20Figar)%20who%20aspires%20to%20be%20India's%20law%20minister%2C%20a%20healer%20(Alpana%20Buch)%20who%20runs%20a%20shady%20trust%20that%20receives%20donations%20from%20the%20Kotharis%2C%20Indrani's%20best%20friend%20Dolly%20Bhatia%20(Waluscha%20De%20Sousa)%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Indrani's%20immediate%20family%20-%20are%20in%20Karma's%20line%20of%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndrani%20and%20Kaushal's%20marriage%20hangs%20by%20a%20thread%2C%20their%20son%20has%20no%20patience%20for%20his%20mother's%20ways%2C%20and%20the%20daughter%20is%20a%20rebel%20determined%20not%20to%20play%20by%20the%20rules%20her%20mom%20sets.%20The%20two%20Kothari%20scions%20spark%20many%20a%20crisis%20as%20they%20seek%20to%20dismantle%20the%20social%20barriers%20that%20prevent%20them%20from%20venturing%20forth%20into%20the%20world%20and%20doing%20their%20own%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarma%20schemes%20incessantly.%20She%20receives%20help%2C%20most%20of%20it%20unsolicited%2C%20from%20flamboyant%20entrepreneur%20Zane%20Khan%20(Viraf%20Patell).%20The%20man%20has%20links%20with%20her%20unhappy%20past.%20So%20does%20cafe%20owner%20Vedant%20Koli%20(debutant%20Rachit%20Singh).%20With%20neither%20of%20the%20two%20men%20is%20Karma's%20relationship%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Karma%20and%20Ahaan%20drift%20into%20a%20tentative%20relationship%2C%20trouble%20mounts%20for%20the%20Kotharis%20and%20their%20acquaintances.%20The%20revenge-seeker's%20acts%20often%20threaten%20to%20recoil%20on%20her.%20But%20she%20is%20determined%20not%20to%20be%20deflected%20from%20her%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%20a%20cakewalk.%20The%20woman%20Karma%20is%20up%20against%20is%20a%20formidable%20adversary%20not%20given%20to%20half%20measures.%20That%20apart%2C%20the%20latter's%20right-hand%20man%20is%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20any%20length%20to%20protect%20his%20boss.%20The%20battle%20of%20attrition%20between%20the%20two%20women%20serves%20the%20purpose%20of%20driving%20the%20series%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20%3Cem%3EKarmma%20Calling%3C%2Fem%3E%20darts%20from%20one%20thing%20to%20another%2C%20it%20frequently%20flounders%20and%20loses%20its%20way.%20Over-explication%20of%20character%20motives%20and%20plot%20points%20blunts%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20tale%20and%20pushes%20the%20series%20into%20a%20rather%20jaded%20loop.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20second%20web%20series%2C%20Raveena%20Tandon%20is%20the%20pivot.%20She%20does%20not%20stop%20trying%20to%20hold%20Karmma%20Calling%20together%20but%20finds%20little%20significant%20support%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20cast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20most%20of%20the%20actors%2C%20including%20Namrata%20Sheth%2C%20who%20plays%20the%20show's%20principal%20character%2C%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20is%20nothing%20to%20write%20home%20about.%20They%20are%20adequate%20at%20best%20as%20they%20wait%20and%20wait%20for%20a%20miracle%20to%20occur%20and%20amp%20up%20the%20proceedings.%20Since%20that%20never%20happens%2C%20all%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20is%20left%20to%20Raveena%20Tandon.%20It%20weighs%20her%20-%20and%20the%20series%20-%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706254200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Frh9lahdo_raveena-_