%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Factress-kim-yoo-jung-amazes-fans-with-acting-anniversary-footage-from-my-demon-set%2Farticleshow%2F107164523.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Was%20Kenneth%20Eugene%20Smith%2C%20US%20Prisoner%20Executed%20With%20Nitrogen%20Gas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20US%20state%20of%20Alabama%20on%20Thursday%20put%20to%20death%20a%20convicted%20murderer%20using%20nitrogen%20gas.%20It's%20the%20first%20time%20the%20controversial%20method%20-%20criticised%20by%20human%20rights%20advocates%20-%20has%20been%20used%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKenneth%20Eugene%20Smith%20was%20executed%20by%20a%20method%20called%20nitrogen%20hypoxia%2C%20which%20involves%20pumping%20nitrogen%20gas%20into%20a%20facemask%2C%20causing%20the%20person%20to%20suffocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Murder%20Convict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%2C%2058%2C%20was%20on%20death%20row%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20after%20being%20convicted%20of%20the%201988%20murder-for-hire%20of%20a%20pastor's%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%20and%20his%20aide%2C%20John%20Parker%2C%20were%20convicted%20of%20the%201988%20murder%20of%20Elizabeth%20Sennett%20for%20which%20they%20were%20each%20paid%20%241%2C000.%20Parker%20was%20executed%20by%20lethal%20injection%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharles%20Sennett%2C%20who%20had%20hired%20Smith%20and%20Parker%20for%20his%20wife's%20murder%2C%20killed%20himself%20a%20week%20after%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%20was%20subjected%20to%20a%20botched%20execution%20attempt%20in%202022%2C%20when%20prison%20officials%20were%20unable%20to%20set%20intravenous%20lines%20to%20administer%20a%20lethal%20injection.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20National%20Public%20Radio%20in%20December%20last%20year%2C%20Smith%20had%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20terrified%26quot%3B%20about%20his%20upcoming%20execution%20and%20was%20still%20suffering%20%26quot%3Btrauma%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20previous%20failed%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Was%20He%20Executed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20respirator%20mask%20was%20placed%20over%20his%20face%20to%20pump%20pure%20nitrogen%20to%20pump%20into%20his%20lungs%20instead%20of%20oxygen.%20The%20process%20lasted%20for%20about%2022%20minutes%20before%20he%20suffocated%20to%20death%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%26quot%3Bbegan%20writhing%20and%20thrashing%20for%20approximately%20two%20to%20four%20minutes%2C%20followed%20by%20around%20five%20minutes%20of%20heavy%20breathing%2C%26quot%3B%20media%20witnesses%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlabama%20Department%20of%20Corrections%20Commissioner%20John%20Hamm%20told%20reporters%20that%20it%20appeared%20Smith%20was%20%26quot%3Bholding%20his%20breath%20as%20long%20as%20he%20could%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Binvoluntary%20movement%26quot%3B%20and%20gasping%2C%20which%20was%20%26quot%3Bexpected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%20had%20a%20last%20meal%20of%20steak%2C%20hash%20browns%20and%20eggs%20Thursday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHis%20Last%20Words%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%20and%20other%20relatives%20were%20present%20at%20his%20execution%20when%20he%20gestured%20towards%20them%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20you.%26quot%3B%20Five%20journalists%20were%20allowed%20to%20watch%20the%20execution%20through%20glass%20as%20media%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith's%20last%20words%20were%2C%20%26quot%3BTonight%2C%20Alabama%20caused%20humanity%20to%20take%20a%20step%20backward%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20CBS%2C%20whose%20reporter%20witnessed%20the%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706253960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F24lfpqgo_us-man_625x300_26_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-ne