20this%20case.%20He%20termed%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfailure%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20registry%20to%20list%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20disturbing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cregistry%E2%80%9D%20refers%20to%20the%20administrative%20office%20or%20department%20responsible%20for%20managing%20and%20maintaining%20records%2C%20schedules%2C%20and%20other%20administrative%20tasks%20related%20to%20court%20cases.%20In%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20the%20registry%20plays%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20handling%20the%20paperwork%2C%20scheduling%20hearings%2C%20and%20ensuring%20the%20overall%20administrative%20efficiency%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20registry%20is%20typically%20composed%20of%20court%20officers%20and%20administrative%20staff%20responsible%20for%20processing%20and%20managing%20case%20files%2C%20maintaining%20court%20records%2C%20scheduling%20hearings%2C%20and%20implementing%20the%20decisions%20and%20orders%20of%20the%20court.%20The%20registrar%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20heads%20the%20registry%2C%20which%20is%20answerable%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20as%20he%20is%20the%20master%20of%20the%20roster.%20The%20CJI%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmaster%20of%20the%20roster%E2%80%9D%2C%20can%20assign%20cases%20to%20other%20judges.%20The%20registry%20then%20makes%20allocations%20based%20on%20the%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Dushyant%20Dave%20had%20brought%20to%20light%20the%20non-listing%20of%20the%20Adani%20Power%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20This%20had%20triggered%20wider%20concern%20and%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20registry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20case%20involves%20serious%20allegations%20from%20Jaipur%20Vidyut%20Vitran%20Nigam%20Limited%20concerning%20procedural%20irregularities%20and%20the%20possible%20re-evaluation%20of%20a%202020%20judgment%20without%20following%20proper%20legal%20procedures.%20This%20concern%20centres%20around%20the%20improper%20listing%20of%20an%20application%20by%20Adani%20Power%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Jaipur%20Vidyut%20Vitran%20Nigam%20Limited%2C%20seeks%20a%20review%20of%20the%202020%20judgment%20after%20a%20considerable%20lapse%20of%20more%20than%20two%20years%20without%20filing%20a%20formal%20review%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20deepened%20as%20Dave%20said%20that%20instructions%20were%20given%20to%20avoid%20listing%20the%20case.%20Justice%20Aniruddha%20Bose%20and%20Justice%20P.V.%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20assured%20Dave%20they%20would%20investigate%20the%20matter.%20The%20case%20was%20listed%20for%20hearing%20on%20January%2024%C2%A0%20(Wednesday)%20on%20a%20priority%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20fairness%20and%20transparency%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20these%20concerns%20could%20be%20a%20crucial%20determinant%20to%20ensure%20a%20fair%2C%20transparent%20and%20swift%20resolution%20for%20the%20parties%20involved.%20Analysts%20say%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20uphold%20public%20trust%20in%20the%20judicial%20system.%20The%20outcome%20of%20the%20Adani%20Power%20case%20will%20set%20a%20precedent%20for%20future%20proceedings%20and%20significantly%20influence%20public%20perception%20of%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Advocate%20Dushyant%20Dave%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20over%20potential%20government%20interference%20and%20failing%20to%20list%20the%20case%20underscore%20broader%20issues%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20registry.%20His%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fpdf_upload%2Fletter-to-honble-chieh-justice-of-india-dated-6th-december-09-27-508128.pdf%5C%22%3Eopen%20letter%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%202023%20highlighted%20concern%20over%20where%20he%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20would%20not%20be%20out%20of%20place%20to%20mention%20that%20these%20matters%20include%20some%20sensitive%20matters%20involving%20human%20rights%2C%20Freedom%20of%20Speech%2C%20Democracy%2C%20and%20Functioning%20of%20Statutory%20and%20Constitutional%20Institutions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open%20letter%20urged%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20to%20take%20corrective%20measures%20promptly%20and%20address%20the%20misgivings%20of%20the%20legal%20community.%20Dave%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20recent%20improprieties%20risk%20tarnishing%20the%20institution%E2%80%99s%20respect%20and%20urged%20immediate%20action%20to%20maintain%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20credibility%20under%20the%20Chief%20Justice%E2%80%99s%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Dave%2C%20the%20Handbook%20on%20Practice%20and%20Procedure%20and%20Office%20Procedure%2C%20published%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202017%2C%20clearly%20outlines%20that%20a%20case%20should%20be%20listed%20before%20the%20junior%20judge%20only%20if%20the%20senior%20judge%20is%20unavailable.%20However%2C%20the%20alleged%20violation%20of%20this%20practice%2C%20as%20pointed%20out%20by%20Dave%20and%20if%20true%2C%20raises%20concerns%20about%20the%20adherence%20to%20established%20rules%20within%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20Dave%20highlighted%20the%20role%20of%20CJI%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98master%20of%20the%20roster%E2%80%99.%20This%20running%20issue%20has%20plagued%20the%20system%20well%20before%20Justice%20D%20Y%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20Notably%2C%20the%20handbook%20grants%20the%20CJI%20the%20authority%20to%20list%20cases%20in%20the%20event%20of%20the%20non-availability%20of%20a%20single%20judge%20or%20members%20of%20the%20bench%20due%20to%20retirement%20or%20other%20reasons.%20Such%20cases%20are%20typically%20listed%20per%20subject%20category%20through%20computer%20allocation%20unless%20otherwise%20ordered%20by%20the%20CJI.%20Importantly%2C%20a%20specific%20note%20in%20the%20handbook%20affirms%20the%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20power%20to%20allocate%20or%20assign%20any%20appeal%2C%20cause%2C%20or%20matter%20to%20any%20judge%20or%20court%20judges%2C%20granting%20extraordinary%20flexibility%20in%20case%20distribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDave%20contends%20that%20while%20the%20CJI%20holds%20power%20to%20allocate%20cases%2C%20this%20authority%20is%20contingent%20on%20adherence%20to%20established%20practices%20and%20only%20applicable%20when%20the%20coram%20as%20per%20roster%20is%20unavailable.%20He%20argued%20that%20exercising%20this%20power%20to%20remove%20a%20case%20from%20an%20available%20coram%20and%20place%20it%20before%20another%20is%20a%20deviation%20from%20the%20established%20norms%20of%20the%20top%20court.%20Expressing%20regrets%20for%20resorting%20to%20an%20open%20letter%2C%20Dave%20had%20noted%20the%20lack%20of%20response%20to%20emails%20raising%20grievances%20about%20the%20issue%2C%20sent%20in%20by%20lawyers%20to%20the%20registrar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstances%20detailed%20in%20Dave%E2%80%99s%20letter%20point%20to%20a%20significant%20deviation%20from%20customary%20procedures%20within%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20As%20his%20letter%20highlighted%2C%20the%20abrupt%20transfer%20of%20cases%20between%20different%20benches%20signifies%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20established%20norms%20of%20the%20apex%20court.%20This%20departure%20becomes%20even%20more%20evident%20when%20considering%20an%20analysis%20conducted%20by%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farticle-14.com%2Fpost%2Fcontrary-to-sc-s-rules-of-assignment-at-least-8-politically-sensitive-cases-moved-to-one-judge-in-4-months-65713ae124602%5C%22%3EArticle%2014%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20brings%20to%20light%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20pattern%20over%20a%20four-month%20period%20wherein%20politically%20sensitive%20cases%20like%20JNU%20scholar%20Umar%20Khalid%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%20and%20challenges%20to%20UAPA%20were%20redirected%20to%20a%20particular%20bench.%20Such%20practices%20must%20be%20compatible%20with%20the%20established%20rules%20and%20procedures%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20prompting%20questions%20about%20the%20adherence%20to%20fair%20and%20transparent%20judicial%20processes%20in%20handling%20these%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVishal%20Vaibhav%20Singh%20is%20a%20student%20at%20the%20National%20Law%20University%2C%20Odisha%20and%20an%20aspiring%20litigator.%20He%20is%20an%20intern%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706253354000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-raises-concerns-over-adani-power-case-listing-dushyant-dave-alleges-contempt%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Adani%20Power%20case%20not%20being%20listed%20has%20raised%20concerns%20beyond%20this%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-raises-concerns-over-adani-power-case-listing-dushyant-dave-alleges-contempt%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Military%20prowess%2C%20Nari%20Shakti%20on%20full%20display%20at%20R-Day%20parade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706253289000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107165535%2Cimgsize-3649487.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F75th-republic-day-military-prowess-and-nari-shakti-at-rday-parade%2Farticleshow%2F107164103.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20year%E2%80%99s%20Republic%20Day%20witnessed%20the%20comeback%20of%20the%20horse-drawn%20%E2%80%98buggy%E2%80%99%20after%20a%20gap%20of%2040%20years%20as%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20her%20French%20counterpart%20Macron%20travelled%20in%20the%20traditional%20carriage%20to%20the%20Kartavya%20Path%20for%20the%20parade.%20The%20women%20dominated%20the%20par