20which%20country%20would%20keep%20the%20buggy%2C%20the%20two%20nations%20came%20up%20with%20a%20unique%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Lucky%20Coin%20Toss%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20neighbours%20left%20the%20decision%20up%20to%20fate%20and%20chose%20simply%20to%20toss%20a%20coin.%20India's%20Colonel%20Thakur%20Govind%20Singh%20and%20Pakistan's%20Sahabzada%20Yaqub%20Khan%20flipped%20the%20coin.%20As%20fate%20would%20have%20it%2C%20Colonel%20Singh%20won%20the%20buggy%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20the%20buggy%20was%20used%20by%20the%20President%20to%20ride%20from%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20to%20Parliament%20for%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony.%20The%20carriage%20was%20also%20used%20to%20ferry%20the%20head%20of%20state%20to%20the%20Beating%20Retreat%20ceremony%20at%20Vijay%20Chowk%20on%20Kartavya%20Path%20to%20mark%20the%20end%20of%20Republic%20Day%20celebrations%20on%20January%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20years%20after%20Independence%2C%20the%20use%20of%20the%20open-carriage%2C%20which%20was%20a%20common%20transport%20vehicle%20for%20the%20President%2C%20was%20discontinued%20owing%20to%20security%20threats.%20The%20traditional%20buggy%20was%20soon%20replaced%20by%20bullet-proof%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20historic%20buggy%20made%20a%20comeback%20in%202014%20with%20President%20Pranab%20Mukherjee%20arriving%20in%20it%20to%20attend%20the%20Beating%20Retreat%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706251680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fef4l79fg_presidential-buggy_625x300_26_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-lucky-coin-toss-with-pakistan-how-india-got-buggy-used-by-president-4935052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20morning%20of%20India's%2075th%20Republic%20Day%20on%20Friday%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20and%20France's%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20travelled%20from%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20grand%20parade%20at%20Kartavya%20Path.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fa-lucky-coin-toss-with-pakistan-how-india-got-buggy-used-by-president-4935052%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22David%2C%20Goliath%2C%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20Part%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26111836%2F1-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EStand-up%20comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra%20noted%20in%20one%20of%20his%20more%20recent%20shows%2C%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20has%20absolute%20clarity%20about%20what%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20needs%20to%20do%20and%20knows%20even%20better%20than%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20what%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20should%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20if%20to%20prove%20the%20truth%20in%20his%20wry%20observation%2C%20media%20commentators%2C%20analysts%20and%20columnists%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20political%20divide%20seem%20to%20be%20convinced%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader%20is%20wasting%20his%20time%20doing%20a%20second%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20this%20close%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConventional%20wisdom%2C%20they%20say%2C%20dictates%20that%20the%20Congress%20should%20not%20be%20wasting%20its%20time%20and%20limited%20resources%20on%20another%20%E2%80%9Cfeel%20good%E2%80%9D%20yatra%2C%20but%20should%20instead%20be%20focusing%20on%20other%20more%20pressing%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20question%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%3A%20What%20good%20is%20conventional%20wisdom%20when%20all%20the%20conventions%20and%20institutions%20that%20make%20for%20a%20healthy%20democracy%20have%20been%20effectively%20hijacked%20by%20the%20government%20in%20power%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20knows%20the%20next%20general%20elections%20will%20be%20an%20unequal%20fight.%20On%20one%20side%20is%20the%20ruling%20party%20with%20big%20money%2C%20big%20media%2C%20and%20all%20the%20investigating%20agencies%20at%20its%20beck%20and%20call%3B%20on%20the%20other%2C%20a%20beleaguered%20and%20fragile%20opposition%20alliance%20under%20relentless%20siege%20by%20the%20state.%20What%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20is%20very%20much%20a%20David%20vs%20Goliath%20faceoff%2C%20the%20ultimate%20metaphor%20for%20unequal%20battles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20be%20useful%20to%20explore%20the%20actual%20battle%20between%20David%20and%20Goliath%20in%20some%20depth.%20In%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EDavid%20and%20Goliath%3A%20Underdogs%2C%20Misfits%20and%20the%20Art%20of%20Battling%20Giants%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20bestselling%20author%20Malcolm%20Gladwell%20has%20elaborated%20at%20some%20length%20on%20the%20historical%20underpinnings%20of%20this%20event%20which%20is%20said%20to%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20ancient%20Palestine%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%2011th%C2%A0century%20BC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fledgling%20kingdom%20of%20Israel%20under%20its%20first%20king%2C%20Saul%2C%20was%20under%20siege%20by%20the%20Philistines%2C%20a%20battle-hardened%2C%20sea-faring%20warrior%20race%20from%20Crete.%20The%20Philistines%20had%20set%20up%20camp%20along%20the%20southern%20ridge%20of%20the%20Elah%20valley%20and%20the%20Israelites%2C%20a%20mountain-dwelling%20people%2C%20had%20pitched%20their%20tents%20along%20the%20northern%20ridge%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20Between%20them%20lay%20a%20ravine.%20Neither%20side%20moved%2C%20for%2C%20to%20attack%20would%20have%20meant%20descending%20into%20the%20ravine%20and%20making%20a%20suicidal%20climb%20up%20the%20enemy%E2%80%99s%20ridge%20up%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiring%20of%20the%20stalemate%2C%20the%20Philistines%20finally%20sent%20their%20most%20terrifying%20warrior%2C%20Goliath%20of%20Gath%2C%20down%20into%20the%20valley%20to%20resolve%20the%20deadlock%20in%20one-on-one%2C%20hand-to-hand%20combat.%20For%2040%20days%20every%20morning%20and%20every%20evening%2C%20Goliath%20shouted%20his%20taunts%20at%20King%20Saul%20and%20the%20army%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Book%20of%20Samuel%2C%20in%20which%20this%20story%20is%20recorded%2C%20notes%20that%20Goliath%20was%20about%20eight%20feet%20tall%2C%20covered%20with%20armour%20from%20head%20to%20toe%20and%20carried%20a%20bronze%20javelin%20capable%20of%20wreaking%20serious%20damage.%20One%20can%20understand%20why%20the%20Israelites%20were%20having%20a%20difficult%20time%20finding%20a%20volunteer%20to%20go%20up%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20till%20David%2C%20a%20young%20shepherd%20with%20no%20military%20experience%20came%20along%20and%20offered%20to%20go%20and%20fight%20the%20giant.%20King%20Saul%20tried%20to%20dissuade%20the%20young%20man%2C%20but%20finally%20unable%20to%20do%20so%2C%20offered%20David%20his%20own%20armour.%20David%20tried%20it%20on%20but%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20walk%20in%20these%20for%20I%20am%20unused%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20Stands%20for%20Endangered%20Constitutional%20Values%3A%20Yogendra%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-bharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-yogendra-yadav-assam%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20Stands%20for%20Endangered%20Constitutional%20Values%3A%20Yogendra%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Goliath%20saw%20David%20approaching%2C%20he%20roared%2C%20%E2%80%9CAm%20I%20a%20dog%20that%20you%20should%20come%20to%20me%20with%20sticks%3F%E2%80%9D%20What%20happened%20next%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20history.%20David%20picked%20up%20five%20smooth%20stones%20from%20the%20riverbed%2C%20loaded%20one%20into%20his%20slingshot%2C%20ran%20towards%20Goliath%20and%20let%20fly.%20The%20stone%20found%20its%20mark%20%E2%80%93%20right%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20Goliath%E2%80%99s%20forehead%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20giant%20crumpled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20book%2C%20Gladwell%20mentions%20Eitan%20Hirsch%2C%20a%20ballistics%20expert%20who%20did%20a%20series%20of%20calculations%20showing%20that%20a%20typical-size%20stone%20hurled%20by%20an%20expert%20slinger%20at%20a%20distance%20of%2035%20metres%20would%20have%20hit%20Goliath%E2%80%99s%20head%20with%20a%20velocity%20of%2034%20metres%20per%20second%20%E2%80%93%20more%20than%20enough%20to%20penetrate%20his%20skull%20and%20render%20him%20unconscious%20or%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20even%20more%20interesting%20is%20what%20many%20medical%20experts%20now%20believe.%20Gladwell%20explains%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGoliath%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20had%20a%20serious%20medical%20condition%20called%20acromegaly%E2%80%94a%20disease%20caused%20by%20a%20benign%20tumor%20of%20the%20pituitary%20gland.%20The%20tumor%20causes%20an%20overproduction%20of%20human%20growth%20hormone%2C%20which%20would%20explain%20Goliath%E2%80%99s%20extraordinary%20size.%20(The%20tallest%20person%20in%20history%2C%20Robert%20Wadlow%2C%20suffered%20from%20acromegaly.%20At%20his%20death%2C%20he%20was%20eight%20foot%20eleven%20inches%2C%20and%20apparently%20still%20growing.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20common%20side%20effects%20of%20acromegaly%20is%20vision%20problems.%20Pituitary%20tumors%20can%20grow%20to%20the%20point%20where%20they%20compress%20the%20nerves%20leading%20to%20the%20eyes%2C%20with%20the%20result%20that%20people%20with%20acromegaly%20often%20suffer%20from%20severely%20restricted%20sight%20and%20diplopia%2C%20or%20double%20vision.%20Why%20was%20Goliath%20led%20onto%20the%20valley%20floor%20by%20an%20attendant%3F%20Because%20the%20attendant%20was%20his%20visual%20guide.%20Why%20does%20he%20move%20so%20slowly%3F%20Because%20the%20world%20around%20him%20is%20a%20blur.%20Why%20does%20it%20take%20him%20so%20long%20to%20understand%20that%20David%20has%20changed%20the%20rules%3F%20Because%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20see%20David%20until%20David%20is%20up%20close.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20David%20won%20because%20he%20changed%20the%20rules%20of%20engagement.%20And%20Goliath%20lost%20because%20he%20quite%20literally%20did%20not%20see%20David%20coming%20or%20anticipate%20his%20speed%20and%20agility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20%3Cem%3Egodi%3C%2Fem%3E%20media%20channels%20have%20already%20declared%20Narendra%20Modi%20the%20winner%20of%202024%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20after%20the%20grand%20and%20carefully%20choreographed%20%3Cem%3Epran%20pratishtha%3C%2Fem%3E%20ceremony%20at%20the%20much%20awaited%20(and%20currently%20unfinished)%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%20is%20not%20a%20conventional%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20doing%20exactly%20what%20a%20leader%20of%20an%20opposition%20party%20needs%20to%20do%20at%20this%20critical%20juncture%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%3A%20bypassing%20the%20restrictions%20of%20state-controlled%20media%2C%20personally%20connecting%20with%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20raising%20five%20key%20issues%20of%20social%20justice%20%E2%80%93%20justice%20for%20the%20youth%2C%20equal%20representation%2C%20justice%20for%20women%2C%20justice%20for%20farmers%20and%20justice%20for%20labourers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchart-ahead-of-indias-election-what-do-people-care-about%5C%22%3Erecent%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Statista%20Consumer%20Insights%2C%20these%20are%20fundamentally%20the%20same%20issues%20that%2024%2C000%20online%20respondents%20consider%20to%20be%20the%20most%20pressing%3A%20unemployment%2C%20education%2C%20poverty%20and%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20challenging%20phases%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20are%20yet%20to%20come%20as%20it%20passes%20through%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-ruled%20states%2C%20but%20judging%20by%20both%20the%20enthusiastic%20respo