t%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20PTI%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20always%20used%20to%20motivate%20me%20whenever%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20low.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20dedicate%20my%20success%20to%20my%20parents%2C%20family%20and%20faculty%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20preparation%20strategy%2C%20she%20said%2C%20she%20would%20study%20for%2012-13%20hours%20every%20day.%20Ms%20Sree%20also%20planned%20to%20take%20up%20Computer%20Science%20in%20IIT%20Bombay%20and%20later%20do%20research%20in%20Mathematics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20I%20could%20have%20got%20a%20better%20rank.%20I%20expected%20top%2010.%20I%20used%20to%20study%2012-13%20hours%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%20entrance%20exam%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C80%2C372%20appeared%20in%20both%20papers%20in%20IIT-JEE%20Advanced.%20Of%20these%2C%20around%2043%2C773%20students%20qualified.%20As%20many%20as%2036%2C204%20male%20students%20and%207%2C509%20female%20students%20cleared%20JEE%20Advanced%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706250480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-01%2Fqb6ie6d_jee-exam_625x300_30_January_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fjee-mains-2024-meet-jee-toppers-2023-know-their-preparation-strategy-4934944%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202023%20entrance%20exam%2C%20a%20total%20of%201%2C80%2C372%20appeared%20in%20both%20papers%20in%20IIT-JEE%20Advanced.%20Of%20these%2C%20around%2043%2C773%20students%20qualified.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fjee-mains-2024-meet-jee-toppers-2023-know-their-preparation-strategy-4934944%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fjee-mains-2024-meet-jee-toppers-2023-know-their-preparation-strategy-4934944%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fjee-mains-2024-meet-jee-toppers-2023-know-their-preparation-strategy-4934944%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20'Rocket%20Girls'%20Create%20History%20At%20Republic%20Day%20Parade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20rocket%20girls%20have%20made%20us%20proud%20and%20now%20they%20have%20basked%20in%20glory%20at%20the%20Republic%20Day%20Parade%20as%20the%20space%20agency's%20tableau%20'Chandrayaan-3%20-%20A%20Saga%20in%20the%20Indian%20Space%20History'%20ambled%20down%20Kartavya%20Path%2C%20bringing%20cheers%20and%20smiles%20to%20everyone%20present%20at%20the%20venue.%20%3Cem%3ENari%20Shakti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20on%20full%20display%20at%20this%20year's%20parade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20women%20scientists%20waved%20to%20the%20crowd%20from%20the%20tableau%20that%20showed%20the%20Shiv-Shakti%20Point%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20the%20Vikram%20Lander%20and%20Pragyan%20rover%2C%20and%20another%20220%20women%20scientists%20from%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20who%20were%20special%20invitees%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%20gala%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20can%20soon%20have%20a%20woman%20astronaut%2C%20asserts%20Shri%20S%20Somanath%2C%20Chairman%2C%20ISRO%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20first%20flight%20of%20Gaganyaan%2C%20it%20may%20well%20be%20an%20all-male%20crew%20but%20as%20and%20when%20women%20test%20pilots%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20are%20available%2C%20we%20can%20have%20Indian%20women%20as%20astronauts%20on%20an%20Indian%20mission.%20ISRO%20will%20welcome%20women%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20Gaganyaan%20astronaut%20corps%2C%20and%20also%20as%20mission%20specialists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20tableau%20also%20showed%20the%20landmark%20Aditya%20L1%20mission%20that%20was%20led%20by%20a%20woman%3B%20a%20model%20of%20India's%20'Bahubali%20rocket'%20the%20Launch%20Vehicle%20Mark%203%20and%20an%20image%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antrisha%20Station%20and%20a%20depiction%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20program.%20The%20float%20also%20does%20not%20forget%20to%20depict%20ancient%20astronomers%20and%20space%20pioneers%20like%20Aryabhata%20and%20Varahamihir%20on%20murals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20what%20many%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20gender%20bias%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Space%2C%20Ms%20Nigar%20Shaji%20while%20earlier%20speaking%20to%20NDTV%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20glass%20ceiling%20for%20women%20at%20ISRO%2C%20adding%20that%20at%20ISRO%20only%20talent%20matters%2C%20gender%20plays%20no%20role.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20one%20among%20many%20'sheroes'%20at%20ISRO.%20Earlier%20Ms%20M%20Vanitha%20led%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20and%20Ms%20Thenmozhi%20Selvi%20K%20led%20the%20making%20of%20the%20earth%20imaging%20satellite%2C%20OceanSAT.%20More%20recently%2C%20Ms%20Kalpana%20K%20has%20been%20deputy%20project%20director%20for%20the%20highly%20successful%20ongoing%20Chandrayaan-3%20mission.%20On%20the%20shop%20floor%20and%20clean%20rooms%20of%20ISRO%2C%20men%20and%20women%20work%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20bring%20glory%20to%20India.%20All%20'rocket%20girls'%20who%20quietly%20and%20humbly%20do%20their%20jobs%20to%20make%20India%20a%20proud%20space%20fairing%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Somanath%2C%20says%20today%20that%20about%20one-fifth%20of%20the%20workforce%20at%20the%20space%20agency%20are%20women%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20have%20more%20women%20on%20the%20rolls%2C%20but%20vehemently%20insists%20that%20%26quot%3Bat%20ISRO%20gender%20plays%20no%20role%2C%20only%20talent%20matters%20and%20the%20right%20person%20is%20carefully%20chosen%20to%20do%20the%20precise%20job.%20Even%20the%20administrative%20staff%20give%20their%20best.%20This%20is%20what%20makes%20ISRO%20stand%20out%20and%20shine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20engineer%20Ms%20K%20Thenmozhi%20Selvi%20has%20made%2010%20satellites%20in%20her%20long%20career%20at%20ISRO.%20She%20joined%20as%20a%20Technical%20Assistant%20and%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%20to%20head%20the%20making%20of%20the%20several%20hundred%20crore%20OceanSat%20satellite.%20On%20November%2026%2C%202022%20she%20made%20history%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20woman%20ISRO%20engineer%20to%20speak%20from%20the%20podium%20at%20the%20Satish%20Dhawan%20Space%20Center%20at%20Sriharikota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStatistics%20from%20ISRO%20show%20that%20out%20of%20the%2015%2C700%20workforce%2C%20about%2017%25%20of%20women%20make%20up%20the%20technical%20and%20scientific%20cadres%20and%2034%25%20of%20women%20are%20there%20in%20the%20administrative%20cadres%2C%20which%20means%20about%2020%25%20of%20the%20workforce%20at%20ISRO%20are%20women.%20Incidentally%2C%20this%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20national%20average%20for%20other%20science%20departments%20which%20stands%20at%2016.6%20%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20science%20minister%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20recently%20told%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20there%20are%2056%2C747%20full-time%20equivalent%20of%20women%20employed%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%20in%20the%20total%20workforce%20of%203%2C41%2C818%20which%20is%2016.6%25%20of%20total%20S%26amp%3BT%20workforce.%20However%2C%20their%20overall%20participation%20as%20workforce%20including%20research%2C%20auxiliary%2C%20and%20administrative%20role%20in%20R%26amp%3BD%20establishments%20is%20about%2018.8%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20it%20should%20be%2050%20per%20cent%20and%20the%20government%20is%20making%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20bring%20in%20gender%20balance%20through%20special%20women-centric%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20estimate%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20suggests%20that%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20women's%20involvement%20in%20scientific%20research%20has%20increased%20in%20India%2C%20the%20proportion%20of%20female%20researchers%20rose%20from%2013.9%25%20in%202015%20to%2018.7%25%20in%202018.%20However%2C%20there%20were%20fewer%20women%20in%20engineering%20and%20technology%20(14.5%25)%20than%20in%20the%20natural%20sciences%20and%20agriculture%20(22.5%25%20each)%20and%20health%20sciences%20(24.5%25).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20India's%20largest%20civilian%20research%20establishment%2C%20the%20Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20(CSIR)%2C%20is%20today%20for%20the%20first%20time%20headed%20by%20a%20woman%2C%20Dr%20N%20Kalaiselvi%2C%20and%20the%20CSIR%20is%20incidentally%20showcasing%20its%20big%20achievement%20of%20the%20aroma%20mission%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20purple%20revolution%20through%20lavender%20cultivation%20as%20a%20pioneering%20agri-start-up%20women-led%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20'sheroes'%20are%20showing%20how%20nari-shakti%20can%20reach%20new%20orbits%20and%20also%20bring%20peace%20in%20strife-torn%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706250300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4hkbdhto_isro-republic-day-parade-_625x300_26_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-indias-rocket-girls-create-history-at-republic-day-parade-4934931%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20rocket%20girls%20have%20made%20us%20proud%20and%20now%20they%20basked%20in%20the%20glory%20at%20the%20Republic%20Day%20Parade%20as%20the%20space%20agency's%20tableau%20'Chandrayaan-3%20-%20A%20Saga%20in%20the%20Indian%20Space%20History'%20ambled%20down%2C%20bringing%20cheers%20and%20smiles%20to%20everyone.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-indias-rocket-girls-create-history-at-republic-day-parade-4934931%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frepublic-day-2024-indias-rocket-girls-create-history-at-r