3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Republic%20Day%20parade%2C%20as%20PM%20Modi%20arrived%20at%20the%20National%20War%20Memorial%2C%20the%20first%20look%20at%20his%20outfit%20was%20revealed.%20Along%20with%20the%20distinctive%20turban%20he%20was%20seen%20wearing%20a%20white%20kurta%20with%20a%20brown%20coat%20and%20white%20pants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20mark%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Republic%20Day%20programme%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20unfurled%20the%20national%20flag%20at%20the%20Kartavya%20Path.%20The%20flag%20unfurling%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20national%20anthem%20with%20a%20booming%2021-gun%20salute%20given%20with%20the%20indigenous%20gun%20system%20105-mm%20Indian%20Field%20Guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20Mi-17%20IV%20helicopters%20of%20the%20105%20Helicopter%20Unit%20then%20showered%20flower%20petals%20on%20the%20audience%20present%20at%20Kartavya%20Path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20%26quot%3BAavaahan%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20band%20performance%20by%20over%20100%20women%20artists%20playing%20various%20types%20of%20percussion%20instruments%2C%20symbolising%20'Nari%20Shakti'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20is%20in%20attendance%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%2C%20joining%20a%20select%20group%20of%20global%20leaders%20to%20have%20graced%20the%20nation's%20biggest%20ceremonial%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E(With%20agency%20inputs)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706248380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F33mfiq5_pm-modi-turban-republic-day-pti-_625x300_26_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-sports-rajasthani-bandhani-turban-at-republic-day-parade-4934703%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%20occasion%20of%20India's%2075th%20Republic%20Day%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20known%20for%20celebrating%20the%20diverse%20culture%20of%20the%20countr