ter%20with%20parentage%20of%20Pakistani%20origins%2C%20was%20unable%20to%20secure%20a%20visa%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20first%20test%20at%20Hyderabad%20that%20began%2F%20begins%20today.%20Earlier%2C%20Australian%20opener%20Usman%20Khawaja%2C%20who%20also%20has%20Pakistani%20origins%2C%20had%20faced%20the%20same%20troubles%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Indian%20government.%20In%20November%20two%20former%20England%20players%20with%20Pakistani%20parents%20were%20unable%20to%20secure%20visas%20to%20play%20in%20a%20veterans%E2%80%99%20world%20series%20league%20in%20India.%20There%20were%20notable%20difficulties%20with%20the%20visas%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20for%20the%20cricket%20world%20cup%20last%20year%2C%20despite%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20being%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F99af1b03-551a-431a-9a9b-7f0175952a67%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F99af1b03-551a-431a-9a9b-7f0175952a67%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706324104506000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1bdCtn8yJ-7IinFwsvCyXu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edetails%20of%20the%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20simple.%20Bashir%20was%20selected%20by%20the%20England%20cricket%20board%20on%20December%2011%2C%2041%20days%20before%20scheduled%20arrival%20in%20India.%20The%20visa%20application%20process%20started%20immediately%2C%20Bashir%E2%80%99s%20information%20was%20filled%20in%20correctly%20and%20he%20attended%20a%20meeting%20at%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission.%20Another%20was%20cancelled%20by%20officials.%20The%20whole%20England%20squad%20left%20for%20their%20training%20camp%20at%20Abu%20Dhabi%20in%20the%20UAE%20on%20January%2011%20with%20some%20players%2C%20including%20Bashir%2C%20still%20waiting%20on%20visas%20(others%20have%20long-term%20entry%20permission%20from%20previous%20tours%20or%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League).%20Bashir%20was%20assured%20his%20would%20be%20issued%20with%20a%20visa%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%3A%20he%20was%20told%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20would%20have%20to%20fly%20home%20to%20have%20his%20visa%20stamped%20which%20he%20did.%20Bashir%20received%20his%20India%20visa%20yesterday%20and%20is%20expected%20join%20England%E2%80%99s%20Testteam%20in%20India%20over%20the%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20British%20government%2C%20which%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Ff40ae6b0-7a61-41c7-a9e1-d4dd5e1349f5%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2Ff40ae6b0-7a61-41c7-a9e1-d4dd5e1349f5%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706324104506000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2wuNSntoUYyOy5Xj7PdY4q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%20on%20India%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9Ctreat%20British%20citizens%20fairly%20at%20all%20times%20in%20its%20visa%20process%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20previously%20raised%20the%20issues%20British%20citizens%20with%20Pakistani%20heritage%20experience%20applying%20for%20visas%20with%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20London.%E2%80%9D%20Ben%20Stokes%2C%20England%E2%80%99s%20captain%2C%20revealed%20that%20his%20squad%20had%20briefly%20considered%20refusing%20to%20travel%20from%20Abu%20Dhabi%20until%20Bashir%E2%80%99s%20visa%20was%20issued.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20found%20the%20news%20out%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20I%20did%20say%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20fly%20until%20Bash%20gets%20his%20visa.%20But%20that%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20tongue%20in%20cheek.%20I%20know%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20way%20bigger%20thing%20than%20doing%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Stokes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20never%20a%20%5Brealistic%5D%20chance%20that%20we%20were%20ever%20not%20going%20to%20travel%20around%20this%20but%20Bash%20knows%20he%E2%80%99s%20had%20our%20full%20support.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStokes%20is%20right%20that%20no%20cricket%20board%20in%20the%20world%20can%20afford%20to%20offend%20the%20BCCI%2C%20which%20drives%20and%20sustains%20the%20global%20cricket%20carnival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fsri-lankan-legend-ranatunga-calls-out-bcci-over-one-board-one-individual-and-arbitrary-decisions%5C%22%3ESri%20Lankan%20Legend%20Ranatunga%20Calls%20Out%20BCCI%20Over%20%E2%80%98One%20Board%2C%20One%20Individual%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20Arbitrary%20Decisions%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20thus%20surprising%20that%20Stokes%20even%20considered%20the%20idea%20of%20not%20flying%20out%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Bashir%20but%20even%20the%20England%20captain%20would%20not%20have%20been%20sure%20about%20his%20own%20cricket%20board%20standing%20behind%20him.%20Neither%20would%20he%20have%20the%20public%20backing%20of%20the%20bevy%20of%20retired%20England%20cricketers%20looking%20at%20jobs%20as%20cricket%20commentators%20and%20coaches%20with%20the%20BCCI%20and%20the%20IPL.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20reality%20of%20modern%20cricket%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20a%20glimpse%20of%20India%20as%20a%20superpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20is%20run%20by%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20a%20post%20he%20continues%20in%20courtesy%20CJI%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20overturning%20a%20previous%20one%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20it%20acts%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20just%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Any%20respectable%20cricket%20board%20would%20have%20been%20deeply%20embarrassed%20about%20this%20incident%20but%20not%20the%20BCCI%2C%20which%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20further%20the%20ruling%20regime%E2%80%99s%20overt%20anti-Muslim%20agenda%2C%20particularly%20for%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%20Think%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act.%20A%20version%20of%20it%20plays%20out%20in%20the%20visa%20rules%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F306e2a3a-402f-481a-ade1-b51d2b45f80b%3Fj%3DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fredirect%2F306e2a3a-402f-481a-ade1-b51d2b45f80b%3Fj%253DeyJ1IjoiYWt5Mm8ifQ.6MWfvlP9rau_ovHEjX2OsfccTssIZEXNjPP_vKEvs5I%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706324104506000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0C7se2veVlTZJOM9ZYC2Z8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Pakistani%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20those%20of%20Pakistani%20origin.%20The%20rules%20are%20slightly%20different%20for%20even%20Bangladeshi%20citizens.%20Indian%20visa%20forms%20now%20even%20ask%20for%20the%20applicant%E2%80%99s%20religion.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20visa%20process%20for%20Muslims%20from%20these%20two%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20or%20Afghanistan%20%E2%80%93%20have%20no%20meaning%20because%20the%20process%20is%20prima%20facie%20discriminatory%20and%20humiliating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20cricketing%20legend%20like%20Wasim%20Akram%20had%20to%20stop%20working%20with%20IPL%20teams%20in%20India%20because%20of%20the%20humiliating%20process%20of%20police%20reporting%20started%20in%20the%20recent%20years.%20Is%20Akram%20really%20a%20security%20threat%20to%20India%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fcricket-usman-khawaja-icc-bcci-order%5C%22%3EOr%20is%20Usman%20Khawaja%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%20Or%20Shoaib%20Bashir%3F%20Everyone%2C%20including%20those%20running%20the%20BCCI%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20know%20that%20they%20aren%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20reason%20behind%20this%20is%20the%20Hindutva%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20of%20discrimination%2C%20humiliation%20and%20subjugation%20of%20religious%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20from%20the%20territories%20that%20fall%20under%20their%20conception%20of%20Akhand%20Bharat.%20This%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20grave%20insecurity%20and%20outright%20bigotry%2C%20masquerading%20as%20nationalism.%20And%20it%20may%20be%20anything%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESushant%20Singh%20is%20Senior%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706247529000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26110303%2FUntitled-design-2-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-akram-security-threat-usman-khawaja-or-shoaib-bashir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20simple%20reason%20behind%20this%20is%20the%20Hindutva%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20of%20discrimination%2C%20humiliation%20and%20subjugation%20of%20religious%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20from%20the%20territories%20that%20fall%20under%20their%20conception%20of%20Akhand%20Bharat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwasim-akram-security-threat-usman-khawaja-or-shoaib-bashir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lowest%20EPFO%20Registrations%20in%202%20Years%20Signal%20Formal%20Job%20Market%20Decline%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26105531%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20formal%20job%20market%20saw%20a%20decline%20in%20November%2C%202023%20%E2%80%93%20the%20lowest%20figures%20in%20nearly%20two%20years%20for%20some%20funds%20and%20insurances%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fformal-job-additions-decline-further-in-november-mospi%2Farticleshow%2F107147923.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20citing%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Program%20Implementation%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20fresh%20formal%20employment%20creation%20is%20undergoing%20a%20downturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20data%20says%20there%20was%20a%205%25%20drop%20in%20new%20subscribers%20to%20the%20Employees%E2%80%99%20Provident%20Fund%20(EPF)%2C%20to%20736%2C015%2C%20and%20a%2010.5%25%20decline%20in%20the%20Employees%E2%80%99%20State%20Insurance%20Corporation%20(ESIC)%2C%20to%201.16%20million%2C%20compared%20to%20October%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20November%20figures%20essay%20the%20sixth%20consecutive%20month%20of%20decline%2C%20besides%20being%20the%20lowest%20in%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEPFO%20payroll%20data%20helps%20track%20employment%20creation%20in%20the%20formal%20sector%20because%20new%20employees%20must%20sign%20up%20for%20a%20provident%20fund%20under%20the%20EPFO.%20The%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20is%20among%20those%20government%20institutions%20which%20uses%20EPFO%20data%20to%20analyse%20employment%20trends%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20National%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NPS)%20saw%20a%2052%25%20rise%20in%20new%20subscriptions.%20The%20report%20says%20that%20this%20was%20driven%20by%20state%20governments%20and%20Union%20government%20employees%E2%80%99%20share%20has%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20NPS%20subscriptions%20are%20also%20at%20the%20lowest%20in%20nearly%20two%20years%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20number%20of%20jobs%20created%20in%20September%20had%20stood%20at%209%2C26%2C%20934%2C%20the%20number%20had%20reduced%20to%207%2C72%2C084%20in%20October%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fat-7-month-low-job-creation-in-formal-sector-declined-by-16-7-in-october-epfo-data%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20EPFO%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706247195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F26105531%2FUntitled-design-1-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fepfo-formal-job-market-decline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Preliminary%20data%20says%20there%20was%20a%205%25%20drop%20in%20new%20subscribers%20to%20the%20Employees'%20Provident%20Fund%20(EPF)%20in%20November%2C%20compared%20to%20October.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fepfo-formal-job-market-decline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20Conducts%20'Census'%20on%20People's%20Personal%20Details%2C%20Foreign%20Visits%2C%20Militancy%20Links%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Police%20and%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20asking%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20union%20territory%20to%20fill%20up%20questionnaire%20forms%20seeking%20their%20personal%20details%20without%20any%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20uptown%20Srinagar%20city%20said%20that%20a%20couple%20of%20police%20personnel%20from%20the%20local%20police%20station%20dropped%20in%20at%20his%20home%20earlier%20this%20month.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20cops%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20was%20in%20civvies%2C%20handed%20him%20a%20document%20containing%20a%20list%20of%20questions%20with%20the%20direction%20that%20it%20should%20be%20returned%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20households%20in%20our%20locality%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20fill%20up%20the%20questionnaire%20and%20return%20it%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station.%20It%20has%20worried%20me%20but%20we%20are%20helpless%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20resident%2C%20who%20wished%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20fearing%20reprisal%20from%20authorities%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20resident%20said%20that%20the%20document%20is%20meant%20to%20be%20filled%20by%20the%20head%20of%20the%20family%20along%20with%20their%20phone%20and%20Aadhaar%20numbers%2C%20details%20about%20their%20foreign%20visits%2C%20links%2C%20if%20any%2C%20with%20militancy%2C%20family%20members%20settled%20abroad%2C%20status%20of%20land%20and%20vehicles%20owned%2C%20and%20geographical%20positioning%20of%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20asked%20the%20cops%20about%20the%20reason%2C%20they%20said%20that%20it%20was%20for%20security%20purposes%20and%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20second%20resident%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fsecurity-forces-in-jk-conduct-census-seek-details-such-as-terror-links-cctv-cameras-foreign-ties%2Farticle67776686.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20a%20government%20source%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98census%E2%80%99%20exercise%20will%20%E2%80%9Cminimise%20damage%20to%20property%20and%20protect%20locals%E2%80%9D%20in%20case%20of%20a%20gunfight%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20militants%20or%20a%20law-and-order%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20form%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20police%20and%20security%20forces%20have%20the%20precise%20details.%20The%20Army%20has%20already%20completed%20the%20exercise%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20told%20the%20newspaper%20while%20police%20have%20said%20that%20the%20exercise%20will%20%E2%80%9Cease%20%E2%80%A6%20providing%20services%20(such%20as%20passport%20verification)%20to%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20exercise%20is%20being%20conducted%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20an%20uptick%20in%20targeted%20attacks%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20it%20is%20aimed%20to%20systematise%20police%20records%20about%20individual%20households%20and%20any%20changes%20in%20family%20composition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20residents%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20is%20without%20an%20elected%20government%20since%202018%2C%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20security%20forces%20to%20give%20out%20their%20personal%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20similar%20%E2%80%9Ccensus%E2%80%9D%20form%20was%20distributed%20in%20Srinagar%20by%20the%20police%2C%20prompting%20many%20residents%20to%20allege%20that%20the%20security%20agencies%20were%20conducting%20their%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20profiling%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20was%20forced%20to%20suspend%20a%20similar%20information%20gathering%20exercise%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20following%20a%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20Army%20has%20been%20conducting%20similar%20drives%20in%20rural%20areas%20of%20Kashmir%20where%20houses%20are%20alphanumerically%20marked%20by%20the%20soldiers%20of%20the%20local%20unit%20of%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%2C%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20counter-terrorism%20force%2C%20and%20the%20house%20owners%20are%20warned%20against%20erasing%20these%20markings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20mohalla%20heads%20have%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20get%20complete%20details%20of%20residents%20and%20the%20number%20of%20households%20in%20their%20locality%20by%20the%20army%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CRPF%20had%20also%20conducted%20a%20similar%20survey%20in%20parts%20of%20Kashmir%20last%20year%2C%20reportedly%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20central%20force%20has%20been%20reportedly%20asked%20to%20collect%20the%20details%20in%20their%20respective%20areas%20of%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20%E2%80%98census%E2%80%99%20comes%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20increased%20use%20of%20surveillance%20systems%20in%20Kashmir%20following%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20then%20chief%20of%20Kashmir%20Police%2C%20Vijay%20Kumar%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20force%20was%20aiming%20to%20profile%20%E2%80%9C80%25%20of%20Kashmiris%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20officials%20have%20defended%20these%20exercises%20as%20a%20necessity%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20trouble%2C%20many%20Kashmiri%20residents%20and%20rights%20campaigners%20have%20raised%20fears%20about%20the%20intrusions%20in%20privacy%20and%20misuse%20of%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20already%20has%20details%20about%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20profession%2C%20their%20phone%20number%2C%20passport%20and%20foreign%20visits%2C%20land%20or%20vehicle%20ownership%20and%20others.%20This%20exercise%20is%20obviously%20aimed%20to%20create%20fear.%20Asking%20for%20these%20details%20again%20is%20a%20way%20of%20telling%20us%20that%20we%20are%20watching%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Srinagar%20resident%20quoted%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20introduced%20a%20Global%20Positioning%20System%20gadget%20to%20keep%20a%20track%20of%20the%20terror%20suspects%20who%20are%20released%20on%20bail%20by%20courts%2C%20drawing%20flak%20from%20the%20civil%20rights%20activists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20officials%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comments%20about%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98census%E2%80%99%20exercise.%20One%20police%20official%20said%20that%20the%20exercise%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20new%E2%80%9D%20and%20it%20was%20repeated%20every%20year%20to%20keep%20the%20local%20police%20stations%20updated%20about%20the%20areas%20under%20their%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20witnessed%20a%20spate%20of%20targeted%20attacks%20and%20deadly%20strikes%20on%20security%20forces%20which%20have%20raised%20uncomfortable%20questions%20about%20the%20claims%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%20that%20terrorism%20was%20over%20and%20normalcy%20had%20returned%20since%20the%20region%20was%20split%20and%20downgraded%20into%20a%20union%20territory%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20since%202019%2C%20the%20casualties%20suffered%20by%20security%20forces%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20went%20up%20by%2010%25%20last%20year.%20The%20slain%20included%20high-ranking%20Army%20and%20police%20officers%2C%20thereby%20punching%20holes%20in%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98normalcy%E2%80%99%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706247022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F22153154%2Fsrinagar-2740020_1920.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjk-conducts-census-on-peoples-personal-details-foreign-visits-militancy-links%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20residents%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20is%20without%20an%20elected%20government%20since%202018%2C%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20security%20forces%20to%20give%20out%20their%20personal%20details.%22%2C%22au