%20will%20be%20taken%20after%20examining%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20scheme%20to%20women%20and%20public%20interest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGehlot%E2%80%99s%20scheme%20aimed%20to%20provide%20free%20smartphones%20to%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Female%20students%20Classes%209-12%20within%20all%20government%20schools%20of%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Female%20students%20enrolled%20in%20government%20higher%20education%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Widows%20or%20single%20women%20within%20the%20state%20receiving%20a%20government%20pension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Family%20women%20who%20have%20fulfilled%20100%20working%20days%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%93%20Women%20who%20have%20completed%2050%20working%20days%20under%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Urban%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20women%20from%20families%20registered%20under%20the%20Chiranjivi%20schemes%20were%20also%20eligible%20to%20receive%20free%20smartphones.%20Currently%2C%20there%20are%201.33%20crore%20families%20registered%20under%20the%20Chiranjivi%20schemes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20Congress-era%20scheme%20halted%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20on%20December%2025%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20issued%20a%20notification%20to%20stop%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Yuva%20Mitra%20Internship%20Programme%2C%20operational%20since%202021.%20The%20government%20had%20enrolled%20around%2050%2C000%20youngsters%20under%20the%20programme%2C%20and%20they%20were%20receiving%20a%20stipend%20of%20more%20than%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%20under%20the%20scheme.%20The%20move%20to%20end%20this%20scheme%20had%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-youth-protest-against-bjp-govts-move-to-discontinue-rajiv-yuva-mitra-scheme%5C%22%3Emet%20with%20protests%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%