eport%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20has%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%20existed%20there%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%20(the%20mosque)%20and%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20temple%20were%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Islamic%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20carried%20out%20a%20court-approved%20scientific%20survey%20of%20the%2017th-century%20mosque%20adjoining%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20to%20determine%20if%20it%20was%20constructed%20over%20a%20pre-existing%20structure%20of%20a%20temple%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20Hindu%20petitioners%20who%20have%20sought%20year-round%20access%20for%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Epooja%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20compound.%20The%20Varanasi%20court%20had%20on%20January%2024%20allowed%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20ASI%20report%20to%20be%20made%20available%20to%20all%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20full%20839-page%20report%20is%20not%20yet%20accessible%2C%20some%20operative%20parts%20of%20the%20ASI%20report%20said%20it%20had%20concluded%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20can%20be%20said%20that%20there%20existed%20a%20large%20Hindu%20temple%2C%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ASI%20said%20it%20drew%20the%20conclusion%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20scientific%20survey%2C%20study%20of%20architectural%20remains%2C%20exposed%20features%20and%20artefacts%2C%20inscriptions%2C%20art%20and%20sculptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20based%20its%20findings%20on%20the%20observations%20and%20scientific%20study%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20chamber%20and%20main%20entrance%20of%20the%20pre-existing%20structure%20in%20existing%20structure%E2%80%9D.%20It%20claimed%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Creuse%20of%20pillars%20and%20pilasters%20of%20pre-existing%20structure%20in%20existing%20structure%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccentral%20chamber%20of%20the%20pre-existing%20structure%20forms%20the%20central%20hall%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%2C%20the%20mosque%2C%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cremaining%20part%20of%20a%20pre-existing%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20ASI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20wall%2C%20made%20of%20stones%20and%20decorated%20with%20horizontal%20mouldings%2C%20is%20formed%20by%20remaining%20parts%20of%20western%20chamber%2C%20western%20projections%20of%20the%20central%20chamber%20and%20western%20walls%20of%20the%20two%20chambers%20on%20its%20north%20and%20south.%20Central%20chamber%20attached%20to%20the%20wall%20still%20exists%20unchanged%20whereas%20modifications%20have%20been%20made%20to%20both%20the%20side%20chambers%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20pillars%20and%20pilasters%20used%20in%20the%20existing%20mosque%20were%20%E2%80%9Creused%20with%20little%20modifications%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20enlargement%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20constructing%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(courtyard).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMinute%20study%20of%20the%20pillars%20and%20pilasters%20in%20the%20corridor%20of%20the%20mosque%20%E2%80%9Csuggest%20that%20they%20were%20originally%20part%20of%20the%20pre-existing%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20ASI%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20their%20reuse%20in%20the%20existing%20structure%2C%20vyala%20figures%20carved%20on%20either%20side%20of%20lotus%20medallion%20were%20mutilated%20and%20after%20removing%20the%20stone%20mass%20from%20the%20corners%20that%20space%20was%20decorated%20with%20floral%20design.%20This%20observation%20is%20supported%20by%20two%20similar%20pilasters%20still%20existing%20on%20the%20northern%20and%20southern%20wall%20of%20the%20western%20chamber%20in%20their%20original%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20during%20its%20survey%20recorded%2034%20inscriptions%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cexisting%20and%20pre-existing%20structures%E2%80%9D%20and%2032%20estampages%20were%20taken.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20inscriptions%20on%20the%20stones%20of%20the%20pre-existing%20Hindu%20temples%2C%20which%20have%20been%20re-used%20during%20the%20construction%2F%20repair%20of%20the%20existing%20structure.%20They%20include%20inscriptions%20in%20Devanagari%2C%20Grantha%2C%20Telugu%20and%20Kannada%20scripts%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20ASI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReuse%20of%20earlier%20inscriptions%20in%20the%20structure%20suggest%20that%20the%20earlier%20structures%20were%20destroyed%20and%20their%20parts%20were%20reused%20in%20construction%20or%20repair%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%2C%20the%20ASI%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20three%20names%20of%20deities%20such%20as%20Janardhana%2C%20Rudra%20and%20Um%C4%93%C5%9Bvara%20were%20found%20in%20these%20inscriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20report%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctemple%E2%80%9D%20had%20a%20big%20central%20chamber%20and%20at%20least%20one%20chamber%20to%20the%20north%2C%20south%20east%20and%20west%20respectively.%20Remains%20of%20three%20chambers%20to%20the%20north%2C%20south%20and%20west%20still%20exist%20but%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20chamber%20to%20the%20east%20and%20any%20further%20extension%20of%20it%20could%20not%20be%20ascertained%20physically%2C%20as%20the%20area%20is%20covered%20under%20a%20platform%20with%20stone%20flooring%2C%20the%20ASI%20noted.%20This%20structure%20with%20thick%20and%20strong%20walls%2C%20along%20with%20all%20architectural%20components%20and%20floral%20decorations%2C%20was%20utilised%20as%20the%20main%20hall%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20it%20claimed%2C%20adding%20that%20animal%20figures%20carved%20at%20the%20lower%20ends%20of%20decorated%20arches%20of%20the%20pre-existing%20structure%20were%20mutilated%2C%20and%20the%20inner%20part%20of%20dome%20is%20decorated%20with%20geometric%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20Tiwari%2C%20lawyer%20for%20Rakhi%20Singh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20five%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20Shringar%20Gauri%20suit%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20ASI%20findings%20%E2%80%9Cestablished%E2%80%9D%20their%20claim%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20temple%20existed%20prior%20to%20the%20existence%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20temple%20structure%20was%20used%20to%20build%20the%20mosque.%20Tiwari%20has%20already%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20pleading%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ewazukhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(place%20of%20ablution)%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20which%20was%20sealed%20in%202022%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20be%20also%20subjected%20to%20a%20similar%20scientific%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20next%20step%20is%20to%20get%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20wazukhana%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3Egarb%20griha%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20old%20temple%20which%20was%20concealed%20behind%20walls.%20Our%20main%20evidence%20is%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%E2%80%99s%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20reacted%20to%20the%20report%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20and%20said%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20ASI%20%E2%80%9Cwouldn%E2%80%99t%20stand%20academic%20scrutiny%20before%20any%20set%20of%20professional%20archaeologists%20or%20historians%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20report%20is%20based%20on%20conjecture%20and%20makes%20a%20mockery%20of%20scientific%20study.%20As%20a%20great%20scholar%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98ASI%20is%20the%20handmaiden%20of%20Hindutva%2C%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20said%20Owaisi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20had%20in%20August%202023%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20conducting%20a%20scientific%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20after%20it%20dismissed%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20committee%E2%80%99s%20petition%20challenging%20the%20Varanasi%20district%20judge%E2%80%99s%20July%2021%20order%20for%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20premises%20by%20the%20ASI.%20The%20district%20judge%20had%20in%20July%20directed%20the%20ASI%20director%20to%20undertake%20scientific%20investigation%2C%20survey%20or%20excavation%20at%20the%20site%2C%20excluding%20the%20areas%20(the%20ablution%20tank)%20sealed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20year.%20The%20district%20court%20had%20also%20directed%20the%20ASI%20to%20conduct%20a%20detailed%20scientific%20investigation%20by%20using%20GPR%20Survey%2C%20excavation%2C%20dating%20method%20and%20other%20modern%20techniques%20of%20the%20present%20structure%20to%20find%20out%20whether%20it%20had%20been%20constructed%20over%20a%20pre-existing%20structure%20of%20a%20Hindu%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20on%20December%2018%20submitted%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover%20its%20report%20of%20a%20scientific%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20premises%20in%20a%20Varanasi%20district%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20had%20earlier%20urged%20the%20district%20judge%20to%20not%20make%20its%20report%20public%20for%20another%20four%20weeks%2C%20citing%20the%20December%2019%20judgment%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20in%20which%20it%20had%20dismissed%20several%20pleas%20of%20the%20UP%20Sunni%20Central%20Waqf%20Board%20and%20the%20masjid%20committee%20challenging%20the%20maintainability%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fexplained-law%2Fallahabad-hc-gyanvapi-case-explained-9074618%2F%5C%22%3Ea%201991%20suit%3C%2Fa%3E%20seeking%20restoration%20of%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20dispute%20raised%20in%20the%20suit%20is%20of%20vital%20national%20importance.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20suit%20between%20the%20two%20individual%20parties.%20It%20affects%20two%20major%20communities%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Rohit%20Ranjan%20Agarwal%20said%20as%20he%20set%20a%20six-month%20deadline%20for%20the%20completion%20of%20proceedings%20in%20a%20Varanasi%20court%20in%20the%201991%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20ruled%20that%20the%20original%20suit%20of%201991%20was%20not%20barred%20by%20provisions%20of%20The%20Places%20of%20Worship%20(Special%20Provisions)%20Act%2C%201991.%20The%20Act%20says%20that%20no%20person%20shall%20convert%20any%20place%20of%20worship%20of%20any%20religious%20denomination%20or%20any%20section%20thereof%20into%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20of%20a%20different%20section%20of%20the%20same%20religious%20denomination%20or%20of%20a%20different%20religious%20denomination%20or%20any%20section%20thereof.%20It%20declares%20that%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20existing%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%20shall%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20suit%20of%201991%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20seeking%20possession%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20premises.%20The%20recent%20suit%20filed%20by%20five%20Hindu%20women%20led%20by%20Rakhi%20Singh%20seeks%20year-round%20access%20for%20darshan%20and%20pooja%20of%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20compound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20on%20December%2019%2C%202023%20also%20directed%20the%20ASI%20to%20submit%20its%20scientific%20survey%20report%20in%20the%201991%20suit%20currently%20heard%20in%20the%20court%20of%20civil%20judge%20senior%20division%2C%20fast%20track.%20In%20case%20it%20was%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20survey%20is%20required%2C%20which%20have%20been%20left%20out%20in%20the%20survey%20conducted%20by%20ASI%2C%20the%20Court%20below%20shall%20issue%20necessary%20directions%E2%80%9D%20to%20carry%20out%20further%20survey%20in%20view%20of%20order%20dated%20April%208%2C%202021%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%203%2C%20the%20ASI%2C%20in%20an%20application%20submitted%20to%20the%20district%20court%2C%20argued%20that%20its%20report%20was%20of%20%E2%80%9Cvital%20importance%E2%80%9D.%20If%20the%20report%20%E2%80%9Cis%20unsealed%20and%20disclosed%20in%20public%E2%80%9D%20before%20the%20submission%20of%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20report%20in%20the%20suit%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Ancient%20Idol%20of%20Swambhu%20Lord%20Vishweshwar%20vs%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%20in%20the%20civil%20judge%2C%20senior%20division%2C%20fast%20track%2C%20there%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20chance%E2%80%9D%20of%20spreading%20%E2%80%9Crumour%20and%20misrepresentation%20in%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20may%20affect%20the%20work%20of%20the%20ASI%2C%20the%20ASI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706238208000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F23142008%2FGyan-vapi-mosque-min.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fasis-survey-report-says-a-large-hindu-temple-existed-under-the-gyanvapi-mosque%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20full%20839-page%20report%20is%20not%20yet%20accessible%2C%20some%20operative%20parts%20of%20the%20ASI%20report%20said%20that%20parts%20of%20a%20temple%20were%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Islamic%20place%20of%20worship.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fasis-survey-report-says-a-large-hindu-temple-existed-under-the-gyanvapi-mosque%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mining%20giants%20told%20to%20pay%20%249.7bn%20over%20Brazil%20dam%20disaster%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706237873000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FD1FC%2Fproduction%2F_90965735_samarco_getty.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fbusiness-68102511%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202015%20collapse%20of%20the%20Fund%C3%A3o%20dam%20in%20Brazil%20caused%20a%20giant%20mudslide%20that%20killed%2019%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2