n%2080-year-old%20grandmother%20to%20take%20care%20of.%20We%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Chennai%20for%20the%20surgery.%20We%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20we%20would%20manage%20the%20next%20meal%20or%20who%20would%20even%20help%20me%20sit%20on%20my%20wheelchair.%20I%20had%20to%20start%20earning%20money%20and%20life%20seemed%20difficult%20all%20over%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Preethi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%2C%20her%20friends%20reiterated%20the%20need%20for%20her%20to%20get%20a%20formal%20degree.%20She%20took%20up%20BSc%20Medical%20Sociology%20as%20it%20had%20no%20practical%20exams.%20She%20also%20did%20MSc%20in%20Psychology%20despite%20wanting%20to%20do%20counselling%20psychology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20counsel%20people%20as%20my%20voice%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20have.%20I%20was%20denied%20admission%20and%20had%20to%20settle%20for%20psychology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20too%20deserve%20a%20life%20of%20dignity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rehabilitation%20is%20provided%20free%20of%20cost%20at%20Soulfree%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FCover-image-13-1705936052-150x79.jpg%201